（加州莫哈維沙漠）

22
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:20,319
（9馬赫）

23
00:04:22,529 --> 00:04:24,698
（彼得“獨行俠”米契爾上校 試飛員）

24
00:04:47,262 --> 00:04:49,056
（管制區）

25
00:05:04,988 --> 00:05:06,156
嘿
Hey.

26
00:05:10,786 --> 00:05:11,787
怎麼回事？
What is it?

27
00:05:14,206 --> 00:05:15,499
怎麼了？
What?

28
00:05:15,582 --> 00:05:18,794
我們奉命禁飛，計畫被取消
We've been ordered to stand down.
They're scrapping the program.

29
00:05:20,045 --> 00:05:22,047
他們說我們沒達標
They say we fell short.

30
00:05:22,130 --> 00:05:24,341
合約門檻是10馬赫
The contract threshold is Mach 10.

31
00:05:24,424 --> 00:05:28,553
那是兩個月後的門檻，今天是9馬赫
Mach 10 is supposed to be in two months.
Today's test point is Mach 9.

32
00:05:28,637 --> 00:05:30,472
這不夠好
Well, that's not good enough.

33
00:05:30,555 --> 00:05:31,932
誰說的？
Says who?

34
00:05:32,015 --> 00:05:33,558
坎恩少將
Admiral Cain.

35
00:05:34,851 --> 00:05:36,311
無人機騎兵
The Drone Ranger.

36
00:05:36,395 --> 00:05:38,897
他要為無人機計畫挪用我們的預算
He wants our budget for his unmanned program.

37
00:05:38,981 --> 00:05:42,484
現在正趕來親自終止今天的試飛
He's on his way to kill the test and shut us down personally.

38
00:05:56,206 --> 00:05:57,791
他還沒到
Well, he isn't here yet.

39
00:06:02,045 --> 00:06:03,380
他們要10馬赫
They want Mach 10,

40
00:06:04,089 --> 00:06:05,299
就給他們10馬赫
let's give 'em Mach 10.

41
00:06:22,065 --> 00:06:23,233
（獨行俠）

42
00:06:23,317 --> 00:06:26,236
記住，合約門檻是10馬赫
Now remember, the contract threshold is Mach 10.

43
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:29,823
不是10.1或10.2，是10馬赫
Not 10.1. Not 10.2. Mach 10.

44
00:06:29,906 --> 00:06:31,908
這樣計畫就可以繼續下去
That should keep the program alive.

45
00:06:34,828 --> 00:06:36,371
我不喜歡你這個表情
I don't like that look, Mav.

46
00:06:38,415 --> 00:06:39,916
我只有這一號表情
It's the only one I got.

47
00:06:48,842 --> 00:06:51,470
這是暗星，收到嗎？
Control, this is Darkstar. How do you read?

48
00:06:51,553 --> 00:06:53,930
這是控制中心，收到了，你呢？
Darkstar, Control. Loud and clear. How me?

49
00:06:54,014 --> 00:06:55,974
收到，完成飛前檢查
Loud and clear. Takeoff precheck's complete.

50
00:06:56,058 --> 00:06:57,267
啟動輔助動力
Ready for APU start.

51
00:06:58,226 --> 00:07:00,020
啟動左引擎
Ready left engine start.

52
00:07:01,772 --> 00:07:03,231
啟動右引擎
Ready right engine start.

53
00:07:04,358 --> 00:07:05,442
滑行準備
Thumbs for taxi.

54
00:07:07,945 --> 00:07:09,613
開始滑行
We are ready for taxi.

55
00:07:11,239 --> 00:07:14,618
塔台，這是暗星，我正準備滑行
Tower, this is Darkstar. We are taxiing with information Alpha.

56
00:07:14,701 --> 00:07:16,620
暗星，可以滑行
Darkstar, you are clear to taxi.

57
00:07:16,703 --> 00:07:19,623
21跑道，風向210，風速10節
Runway 21. Winds 210, 10.

58
00:07:19,706 --> 00:07:22,209
-油溫正常
-同意
-Fuel temps are looking good.
-Control concurs.

59
00:07:22,292 --> 00:07:24,962
電池量95%，艙壓正常
Battery's holding at 95%. Cabin pressure looks good.

60
00:07:25,045 --> 00:07:26,254
同意
Control concurs.

61
00:07:26,338 --> 00:07:27,965
這是暗星，準備起飛
Tower, this is Darkstar. We're ready for takeoff.

62
00:07:28,048 --> 00:07:31,009
要求爬升至600呎以上
Requesting an unrestricted climb to 600 and above.

63
00:07:31,093 --> 00:07:33,512
暗星，儘管起飛吧
Darkstar, the runway and skies are yours.

64
00:07:33,595 --> 00:07:35,639
切斯特坎恩少將
Rear Admiral Chester Cain.

65
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:38,976
獨行俠，坎恩到了大門
Maverick, Cain just pulled up to the gate.

66
00:07:39,726 --> 00:07:41,144
喊卡還來得及
It's not too late to stop, buddy.

67
00:07:42,229 --> 00:07:44,856
你知道這麼做的後果
You know what happens to you if you go through with this.

68
00:07:47,025 --> 00:07:49,486
我知道不這麼做大家都會失業
I know what happens to everyone else if I don't.

69
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:53,740
暗星準備起飛
Darkstar is ready for takeoff.

70
00:07:56,743 --> 00:07:57,869
大夥兒
Everyone,

71
00:07:58,370 --> 00:08:00,622
準備起飛，先從引擎開始
go for takeoff, starting with engine.

72
00:08:00,706 --> 00:08:02,499
-引擎，行
-熱源影像系統，行
-Engine, go.
-Thermals, go.

73
00:08:02,582 --> 00:08:04,668
-燃油，行
-電力系統，行
-Fuel, go.
-Electric, go.

74
00:08:04,751 --> 00:08:06,086
控制面，行
Control surfaces, go.

75
00:08:06,169 --> 00:08:08,880
暗星，你可以起飛
Darkstar, Control. You're cleared for takeoff.

76
00:08:08,964 --> 00:08:10,507
好吧，寶貝
All right, sweetheart,

77
00:08:11,174 --> 00:08:12,342
最後一次飛行
one last ride.

78
00:08:38,076 --> 00:08:42,080
爬升至600呎後，加速到3.5馬赫
Darkstar, you are cleared above 600. Increase to Mach 3.5.

79
00:08:42,163 --> 00:08:46,001
爬升至600呎後，加速到3.5馬赫
Cleared above 600. Increase to Mach 3.5.

80
00:08:52,341 --> 00:08:53,383
少將
Admiral.

81
00:08:54,176 --> 00:08:56,720
-來得剛好
-我提早了，你也是
-Just in time, sir.
-I'm early. So are you.

82
00:08:56,803 --> 00:08:58,263
可以解釋嗎？
You care to explain?

83
00:08:58,347 --> 00:09:00,307
切換到超音速燃燒衝壓引擎
Transitioning to scramjet.

84
00:09:14,696 --> 00:09:16,114
坎恩少將要求…
Mav, Admiral Cain is asking--

85
00:09:16,198 --> 00:09:18,659
-命令
-命令你立刻降落
-Ordering.
-Ordering that we bring her down.

86
00:09:26,249 --> 00:09:27,709
爬升至六…
…within six…

87
00:09:27,793 --> 00:09:29,544
通訊不穩定，長官
This is where we've had trouble with comms, sir.

88
00:09:29,628 --> 00:09:32,005
因為地球曲面差，這叫地球隆起
It's the Earth's curvature. It's called "Earth Bulge."

89
00:09:32,089 --> 00:09:33,423
有人替你倒咖啡嗎？
Did anyone offer you a coffee?

90
00:09:35,175 --> 00:09:36,009
Okay.

91
00:09:43,976 --> 00:09:45,852
達到7馬赫，逼近8馬赫
He's at Mach 7, pushing 8.

92
00:09:45,936 --> 00:09:48,146
-飛行數據？
-數據沒問題
-Flight data?
-Receiving. Data is good.

93
00:09:53,527 --> 00:09:55,904
油溫升高，引擎仍然穩定
Temperature's climbing. Response is still stable.

94
00:09:55,988 --> 00:09:56,822
感覺很好
We're feeling good.

95
00:10:00,617 --> 00:10:01,827
8.8馬赫
Mach 8.8.

96
00:10:02,828 --> 00:10:03,829
8.9
8.9

97
00:10:04,454 --> 00:10:05,747
9馬赫
Mach 9.

98
00:10:05,831 --> 00:10:07,541
他是世上最快的人
He's the fastest man alive.

99
00:10:26,810 --> 00:10:28,437
呆頭鵝，看到了嗎？
Talk to me, Goose.

100
00:10:30,439 --> 00:10:31,565
9.1馬赫
Mach 9.1.

101
00:10:32,566 --> 00:10:33,567
9.2
9.2

102
00:10:40,866 --> 00:10:42,075
9.3馬赫
Mach 9.3.

103
00:10:44,786 --> 00:10:45,996
9.4
9.4

104
00:10:47,497 --> 00:10:49,458
接近超高音速
Approaching high hypersonic.

105
00:11:01,845 --> 00:11:03,388
風擋過熱警示
Windshield hot caution.

106
00:11:12,522 --> 00:11:14,149
機身溫度升高
Surface temp rising.

107
00:11:19,529 --> 00:11:21,490
快啊，寶貝，再快一點
Come on, sweetheart, just a little more.

108
00:11:22,324 --> 00:11:23,367
只差一點了
Just a little.

109
00:11:27,162 --> 00:11:28,038
快啊！
Come on!

110
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:35,504
快啊！
Come on!

111
00:11:41,009 --> 00:11:42,010
10馬赫！
Mach 10!

112
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:46,515
把它放回你的國防預算中！
Put that in your Pentagon budget!

113
00:11:48,433 --> 00:11:49,643
長官
Sir.

114
00:12:01,238 --> 00:12:02,447
噢，不要
Don't do it. Don't do it.

115
00:12:02,531 --> 00:12:03,532
只要…
Just…

116
00:12:05,450 --> 00:12:07,619
再加一把勁
a little push.

117
00:12:11,748 --> 00:12:13,500
慘了
Holy shit.

118
00:12:22,968 --> 00:12:26,013
作為飛官你很帶種
You got some balls, stick jockey.

119
00:12:26,096 --> 00:12:27,514
我不得不承認
I'll give you that.

120
00:12:31,768 --> 00:12:32,936
噢，慘了
Oh, shit.

121
00:12:38,358 --> 00:12:39,234
獨行俠
Maverick.

122
00:12:41,278 --> 00:12:42,571
獨行俠！
Maverick!

123
00:13:32,829 --> 00:13:33,914
謝謝
Thank you.

124
00:13:34,748 --> 00:13:35,916
我在哪裡？
Where am I?

125
00:13:37,376 --> 00:13:38,585
地球
Earth.

126
00:13:53,183 --> 00:13:54,518
獨行俠
Maverick.

127
00:13:55,269 --> 00:13:56,937
三十多年的軍旅生涯
Thirty-plus years of service.

128
00:13:58,146 --> 00:13:59,523
戰功勳章
Combat medals.

129
00:13:59,606 --> 00:14:00,941
獎項無數
Citations.

130
00:14:01,608 --> 00:14:06,029
四十年來唯一擊落三架敵機的人
Only man to shoot down three enemy planes in the last 40 years.

131
00:14:06,697 --> 00:14:08,073
傑出服役勳章
"Distinguished."

132
00:14:08,156 --> 00:14:11,743
傑出服役勳章、傑出服役勳章
"Distinguished." "Distinguished."

133
00:14:13,495 --> 00:14:16,790
但你卻升不了官，也不肯退役
Yet you can't get a promotion, you won't retire,

134
00:14:16,873 --> 00:14:19,918
盡管多次出生入死，卻又死不了
and despite your best efforts, you refuse to die.

135
00:14:20,502 --> 00:14:24,548
早就該成為二星少將，或是參議員
You should be at least a two-star admiral
by now, if not a senator.

136
00:14:25,090 --> 00:14:26,717
但你仍留在這裡
Yet here you are:

137
00:14:28,385 --> 00:14:29,469
上校
Captain.

138
00:14:30,554 --> 00:14:31,888
為什麼？
Why is that?

139
00:14:32,681 --> 00:14:34,308
人生就是如此難解，長官
It's one of life's mysteries, sir.

140
00:14:34,391 --> 00:14:37,894
這不是笑話，我在問你問題
This isn't a joke. I asked you a question.

141
00:14:39,730 --> 00:14:41,565
這是我的歸屬，長官
I'm where I belong, sir.

142
00:14:42,232 --> 00:14:44,776
海軍不這麼認為
Well, the navy doesn't see it that way.

143
00:14:45,819 --> 00:14:46,903
不再是如此
Not anymore.

144
00:14:48,405 --> 00:14:50,115
你試飛的戰機
These planes you've been testing,

145
00:14:50,824 --> 00:14:51,908
上校
Captain,

146
00:14:52,451 --> 00:14:55,454
遲早有一天不再需要飛行員
one day, sooner than later, they won't need pilots at all.

147
00:14:56,204 --> 00:14:59,541
需要吃喝拉撒睡的飛行員
Pilots that need to sleep, eat, take a piss.

148
00:15:01,752 --> 00:15:03,920
違反命令的飛行員
Pilots that disobey orders.

149
00:15:05,380 --> 00:15:08,300
你只是為其他人爭取一些時間
All you did was buy some time for those men out there.

150
00:15:10,385 --> 00:15:11,637
未來近在咫尺
The future is coming,

151
00:15:12,679 --> 00:15:14,514
而你不會參與其中
and you're not in it.

152
00:15:16,433 --> 00:15:18,518
把他帶出基地
Escort this man off the base.

153
00:15:19,686 --> 00:15:24,024
到他的寢室，看著他打包
Take him to his quarters.
Wait with him while he packs his gear.

154
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:29,488
一小時內出發前往北島航空站
I want him on the road to North Island within the hour.

155
00:15:32,741 --> 00:15:34,284
北島航空站？
North Island, sir?

156
00:15:35,243 --> 00:15:37,704
有一通電話來得時機剛剛好
Call came in with impeccable timing,

157
00:15:37,788 --> 00:15:41,458
就在我準備罰你永遠禁飛之前
right as I was driving here
to ground your ass once and for all.

158
00:15:42,918 --> 00:15:45,462
我很不想說，但是…
It galls me to say it, but…

159
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:50,634
只有老天爺和你的守護天使知道原因
for reasons known only to the Almighty

160
00:15:52,636 --> 00:15:55,055
你又被召回捍衛戰士學校
you've been called back to TOPGUN.

161
00:15:59,226 --> 00:16:02,646
-長官？
-解散，上校
-Sir?
-You are dismissed, Captain.

162
00:16:07,901 --> 00:16:09,820
結局是無可避免的，獨行俠
The end is inevitable, Maverick.

163
00:16:10,737 --> 00:16:12,656
你這種飛官總有一天會被淘汰
Your kind is headed for extinction.

164
00:16:16,451 --> 00:16:17,953
也許吧，長官
Maybe so, sir.

165
00:16:19,621 --> 00:16:21,081
但不是今天
But not today.

166
00:16:30,424 --> 00:16:34,052
（加州聖地牙哥，美國戰機城）

167
00:16:57,784 --> 00:17:03,415
（太平洋艦隊 美軍海軍航空隊）

168
00:17:20,849 --> 00:17:25,312
（湯姆“冰人”卡贊斯基
美國太平洋艦隊司令）

169
00:17:26,146 --> 00:17:28,815
彼得“獨行俠”米契爾上校
Captain Pete "Maverick" Mitchell.

170
00:17:29,650 --> 00:17:31,526
你的聲名遠播
Your reputation precedes you.

171
00:17:32,819 --> 00:17:33,862
謝謝你，長官
Thank you, sir.

172
00:17:35,197 --> 00:17:36,657
那不是讚美
Wasn't a compliment.

173
00:17:38,450 --> 00:17:39,451
我是博爾辛普森中將
I'm Admiral Beau Simpson.

174
00:17:39,534 --> 00:17:41,703
航管指揮官，你認識貝茲少將
I'm the Air Boss. I believe you know Admiral Bates.

175
00:17:42,454 --> 00:17:43,413
術士，長官
Warlock, sir.

176
00:17:43,455 --> 00:17:46,208
我沒想到會受邀回來
Must admit, I wasn't expecting an invitation back.

177
00:17:46,291 --> 00:17:48,085
這叫做命令，獨行俠
They're called orders, Maverick.

178
00:17:49,461 --> 00:17:50,963
你們倆有個共通點
You two have something in common.

179
00:17:51,046 --> 00:17:53,840
旋風是1988屆的第一名
Cyclone here was first in his class back in '88.

180
00:17:53,924 --> 00:17:55,884
其實我只是第二名
Actually, sir, I finished second.

181
00:17:56,551 --> 00:17:58,553
別對我期望太高
Just want to manage expectations.

182
00:18:02,766 --> 00:18:04,017
目標…
The target…

183
00:18:06,144 --> 00:18:08,855
是一座違反多方北約協定
is an unsanctioned uranium enrichment plant

184
00:18:08,939 --> 00:18:11,400
未經批准的鈾濃縮工廠
built in violation of a multilateral NATO treaty.

185
00:18:11,483 --> 00:18:14,444
製造的鈾對該地區的盟國
The uranium produced there represents a direct threat

186
00:18:14,528 --> 00:18:15,821
造成直接威脅
to our allies in the region.

187
00:18:15,904 --> 00:18:20,158
國防部要求我們召集攻擊小隊
The Pentagon has tasked us with assembling
a strike team and taking it out

188
00:18:20,242 --> 00:18:21,952
在工廠運作前摧毀它
before it becomes fully operational.

189
00:18:22,995 --> 00:18:26,832
工廠建在位於這座峽谷盡頭的地下碉堡
The plant sits in an underground bunker
at the end of this valley.

190
00:18:26,915 --> 00:18:28,625
那座峽谷無法以GPS定位
Said valley is GPS-jammed

191
00:18:28,709 --> 00:18:31,503
也受到多座地對空飛彈砲台防衛
and defended by an extensive surface-to-air missile array

192
00:18:31,586 --> 00:18:34,256
加上數架第五代戰鬥機
serving a limited number of fifth-generation fighters,

193
00:18:34,339 --> 00:18:38,302
以及多架儲備戰機保衛領空
which in turn are backed up by
a plentiful reserve of surplus aircraft.

194
00:18:38,385 --> 00:18:40,679
包括幾架老舊的F-14戰機
Even a few old F-14s.

195
00:18:40,762 --> 00:18:43,056
不是只有我們保留了老古董
Seems like we're not the only ones holding on to old relics.

196
00:18:44,891 --> 00:18:46,351
上校，你有什麼想法？
What's your read, Captain?

197
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:52,316
通常出動F-35匿蹤戰機就能搞定
Well, sir, normally this would be
a cakewalk for the F-35's stealth,

198
00:18:52,399 --> 00:18:55,110
但無法以GPS定位就沒轍
but the GPS-jamming negates that.

199
00:18:55,193 --> 00:18:58,947
地對空飛彈的存在只能用…
And a surface-to-air threat necessitates
a low-level laser-guided strike

200
00:18:59,031 --> 00:19:00,449
F-18以低空雷射引導攻擊
tailor-made for the F-18.

201
00:19:00,532 --> 00:19:01,533
我認為…
I figure,

202
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:04,202
最少要投擲兩枚精準炸彈
two precision bombs, minimum.

203
00:19:04,286 --> 00:19:06,747
兩架一組，出動四架戰機
Makes it four aircraft flying in pairs.

204
00:19:07,289 --> 00:19:09,499
飛離峽谷必須垂直爬升
That is one hell of a steep climb out of there,

205
00:19:09,583 --> 00:19:11,918
暴露在地對空飛彈攻擊範圍內
exposing you to all the surface-to-air missiles.

206
00:19:12,628 --> 00:19:13,879
就算成功爬升
You survive that,

207
00:19:15,130 --> 00:19:16,757
回程也得一路和敵機交戰
it's a dogfight all the way home.

208
00:19:16,840 --> 00:19:19,468
你擁有這一切的實戰經驗
All requirements for which you have real-world experience.

209
00:19:20,218 --> 00:19:22,304
並不全在同一項任務中
Not in the same mission, sir.

210
00:19:25,057 --> 00:19:26,058
不
No.

211
00:19:28,894 --> 00:19:31,355
有人會無法活著回來
No, someone's not coming back from this.

212
00:19:31,438 --> 00:19:32,898
到底可不可行？
Can it be done or not?

213
00:19:33,565 --> 00:19:35,400
工廠幾時會開始運作？
How soon before the plant becomes operational?

214
00:19:35,484 --> 00:19:37,277
三週後，也許更早
Three weeks. Maybe less.

215
00:19:38,654 --> 00:19:41,281
我很久沒開F-18戰機，而且…
Well, it's been a while since I've flown an F-18, and…

216
00:19:42,282 --> 00:19:44,743
我不確定能信任另外三名飛行員
I'm not sure who I'd trust to fly the other three.

217
00:19:44,826 --> 00:19:46,954
但我會想出辦法
But I'll find a way to make it work.

218
00:19:47,037 --> 00:19:48,705
你誤會了，上校
I think you misunderstand, Captain.

219
00:19:49,414 --> 00:19:50,248
長官？
Sir?

220
00:19:50,332 --> 00:19:53,585
我們不要你飛，而是要你當教官
We don't want you to fly it. We want you to teach it.

221
00:19:56,505 --> 00:19:57,798
教官？
Teach, sir?

222
00:19:59,341 --> 00:20:02,844
我們召回十二名捍衛小組畢業學員
We've recalled 12 TOPGUN graduates from their squadrons.

223
00:20:02,928 --> 00:20:05,639
你要從中細選出六名飛行員
We want you to narrow that pool down to six.

224
00:20:06,306 --> 00:20:07,891
讓他們執行任務
They'll fly the mission.

225
00:20:09,601 --> 00:20:11,019
上校，有問題嗎？
Is there a problem, Captain?

226
00:20:12,938 --> 00:20:15,232
你明知道有…長官
You know there is, sir.

227
00:20:16,441 --> 00:20:17,276
是啊
Yeah.

228
00:20:17,943 --> 00:20:20,445
布萊德利布雷德蕭，也就是公雞
Bradley Bradshaw, aka "Rooster."

229
00:20:20,529 --> 00:20:22,364
你和他老爸曾是搭檔
I understand you used to fly with his old man.

230
00:20:22,447 --> 00:20:24,241
他的呼號是什麼？
What was his call sign?

231
00:20:24,992 --> 00:20:26,618
“呆頭鵝”，長官
"Goose," sir.

232
00:20:26,702 --> 00:20:28,036
他的死是很不幸
Tragic what happened.

233
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:30,038
米契爾上校被裁定沒犯錯
Captain Mitchell was cleared of any wrongdoing.

234
00:20:30,122 --> 00:20:31,957
呆頭鵝的死是意外
Goose's death was an accident.

235
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:33,667
你是這麼想嗎？
Is that how you see it, Captain?

236
00:20:33,750 --> 00:20:35,836
呆頭鵝的兒子也是這麼想嗎？
Is that how Goose's son sees it?

237
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:41,842
恕我直言，長官，我不是教官
With all due respect, sir, I'm not a teacher.

238
00:20:41,925 --> 00:20:43,593
你當過捍衛小組教官
You were a TOPGUN instructor before.

239
00:20:43,677 --> 00:20:46,096
那是三十年前，只撐了兩個月
That was almost 30 years ago. I lasted two months.

240
00:20:46,179 --> 00:20:47,431
我不屬於那裡
It's not where I belong.

241
00:20:47,514 --> 00:20:49,683
我就老實跟你說吧
Then let me be perfectly blunt.

242
00:20:49,766 --> 00:20:53,020
你不是我的首選，其實根本不在名單上
You were not my first choice.
In fact, you weren't even on the list.

243
00:20:53,812 --> 00:20:56,356
舉薦你的人是卡贊斯基上將
You are here at the request of Admiral Kazansky.

244
00:20:57,065 --> 00:21:00,736
我非常景仰冰人
Now, Iceman happens to be a man I deeply admire,

245
00:21:00,819 --> 00:21:03,822
他認為你對海軍仍能有所貢獻
and he seems to think that you have
something left to offer the navy.

246
00:21:04,823 --> 00:21:06,742
我想不出是什麼
What that is, I can't imagine.

247
00:21:08,201 --> 00:21:10,078
你不必接下這工作
You don't have to take this job.

248
00:21:10,162 --> 00:21:11,413
但恕我直言
But let me be clear:

249
00:21:11,496 --> 00:21:14,416
這會是你最後一項任務
This will be your last post, Captain.

250
00:21:16,168 --> 00:21:19,630
當學校的教官，不然就退出海軍
You fly for TOPGUN, or you don't fly for the navy ever again.

251
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:30,015
我賭20塊你不能正中紅心三次
Twenty bucks you can't get three in a row.

252
00:21:42,527 --> 00:21:44,696
（冰人：“怎麼搞得這麼僵？”）

253
00:21:47,866 --> 00:21:53,705
（那個孩子還沒能準備好執行這項任務）

254
00:21:53,789 --> 00:21:55,916
（冰人：“沒有人能

255
00:21:55,999 --> 00:21:58,126
所以才會把你找來”）

256
00:22:01,171 --> 00:22:05,050
（你可以先警告我）

257
00:22:05,133 --> 00:22:08,053
（冰人：“講了你還會來嗎？”）

258
00:22:11,431 --> 00:22:13,642
真不敢相信
Oh, you've got to be kidding me.

259
00:22:16,228 --> 00:22:17,312
彼得
Pete.

260
00:22:18,689 --> 00:22:19,815
潘妮？
Penny?

261
00:22:20,774 --> 00:22:24,194
-妳在這裡幹嘛？
-我才要問你呢
-What are you doing here?
-I should ask you the same thing.

262
00:22:25,445 --> 00:22:27,656
-說來話長
-我不信
-Well, that is a long story.
-I doubt that.

263
00:22:27,739 --> 00:22:28,573
Yeah.

264
00:22:28,657 --> 00:22:30,450
你這次又惹毛了誰？
Who'd you piss off this time?

265
00:22:30,534 --> 00:22:31,952
另一位少將
Another admiral.

266
00:22:32,035 --> 00:22:33,036
那就對了
Exactly.

267
00:22:35,872 --> 00:22:37,916
-妳還在生我氣嗎？
-彼得
-Are you mad at me?
-Oh, Pete.

268
00:22:38,875 --> 00:22:42,045
我沒辦法一直生你氣，那就是問題
I can never stay mad at you. That's the problem.

269
00:22:43,505 --> 00:22:44,798
我得說…
I got to say,

270
00:22:44,881 --> 00:22:48,427
我以為永遠不會在北島航空站碰到你
North Island is the one place
I thought for sure I'd never run into you.

271
00:22:48,927 --> 00:22:51,888
-妳來了多久？
-三年前頂下這地方
-How long you been here?
-Bought this place about three years ago.

272
00:22:51,972 --> 00:22:53,807
-三年前？
-是啊
-Three years?
-Yeah.

273
00:22:53,890 --> 00:22:58,395
就在你惹毛另一位少將被派去沙漠之後
Not long after you got shipped off to the
desert for pissing off that other admiral.

274
00:22:59,313 --> 00:23:01,440
那是三年前的事？
That was three years ago?

275
00:23:02,566 --> 00:23:04,735
你一定惹上大麻煩
You must be in a lot of trouble.

276
00:23:05,319 --> 00:23:07,404
否則不會自願回來這裡
No way you'd come back here willingly.

277
00:23:09,239 --> 00:23:10,240
不過呢…
Well,

278
00:23:11,074 --> 00:23:12,659
你會想辦法解決
you'll sort it out.

279
00:23:13,327 --> 00:23:14,536
不，我想…
No, I think…

280
00:23:15,912 --> 00:23:18,415
-這是最後一次
-少來了
-I think this is it.
-Come on, Pete.

281
00:23:18,498 --> 00:23:21,251
我認識你以後你就一直這麼說
You've been saying that as long as I've known you.

282
00:23:21,335 --> 00:23:24,963
你開F-18載我兜風被逮到也這麼說
You said it after they busted you for
taking me on a joyride in that F-18.

283
00:23:25,547 --> 00:23:27,966
沒過多久你就被派去波士尼亞
Then the next thing I know, you're off to Bosnia.

284
00:23:28,592 --> 00:23:31,178
然後去伊拉克，兩次都有去
Then Iraq. Both times.

285
00:23:31,261 --> 00:23:32,888
你每次惹上麻煩…
You get yourself in trouble,

286
00:23:34,014 --> 00:23:36,892
只要冰人打通電話你又能飛
Iceman makes a call, and you're back in the air.

287
00:23:36,975 --> 00:23:38,518
潘妮，這次不同
Penny, this is different.

288
00:23:38,602 --> 00:23:40,103
彼得，相信我
Pete, trust me,

289
00:23:40,187 --> 00:23:42,439
也許現在看似不可能
as improbable as it seems right now,

290
00:23:42,522 --> 00:23:45,859
但你一定會再坐上戰機出任務
somehow you'll be back in a fighter plane
with your tail on fire.

291
00:23:47,027 --> 00:23:49,029
-潘妮…
-太遲了
-Too late.

292
00:23:49,112 --> 00:23:49,947
什麼？
What?

293
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:52,199
你本來要問我幾點下班
You were about to ask me what time I get off.

294
00:23:55,786 --> 00:23:57,454
別用那副表情看我
Don't give me that look.

295
00:23:58,622 --> 00:24:01,083
我沒用什麼表情看妳，我發誓
I'm not giving you any look. I swear.

296
00:24:01,792 --> 00:24:04,294
我們每次的結局都一樣，彼得
It always ends the same with us, Pete.

297
00:24:05,796 --> 00:24:07,631
這次就別再來一次
Let's not start this time.

298
00:24:12,052 --> 00:24:12,886
好吧
Okay.

299
00:24:13,804 --> 00:24:14,805
很好
Okay.

300
00:24:15,597 --> 00:24:18,513
♪ Put on your red shoes and dance the blues... ♪

301
00:24:19,643 --> 00:24:20,978
妳看起來挺好的
You look good.

302
00:24:31,154 --> 00:24:32,739
多謝了，老兄
Much appreciated, pal.

303
00:24:35,492 --> 00:24:36,576
發生什麼事？
What am I missing?

304
00:24:38,996 --> 00:24:42,916
“冒犯女士、海軍，或把手機放吧台
"Disrespect a lady, the navy,

305
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,876
就得請一輪酒”
"…and you buy a round."

306
00:24:45,460 --> 00:24:46,586
請每一個人？
For everyone?

307
00:24:46,670 --> 00:24:49,423
這就是規矩，幸好時候還早
I'm afraid rules are rules. You're lucky it's early.

308
00:24:50,632 --> 00:24:52,259
拜託！
Oh, come on!

309
00:24:52,843 --> 00:24:54,803
看看誰來了？
What do we have here?

310
00:24:56,513 --> 00:24:58,765
原來是鳳凰
If it ain't Phoenix!

311
00:24:58,849 --> 00:25:01,268
我還以為我們全是菁英，郊狼
And here I thought we were special, Coyote.

312
00:25:02,686 --> 00:25:05,564
沒想到連遜咖都被找來
Turns out the invite went to anyone.

313
00:25:06,356 --> 00:25:07,983
大夥兒，這是捕手
Fellas, this here's Bagman.

314
00:25:08,066 --> 00:25:09,818
-劊子手
-隨便你
-Hangman.
-Whatever.

315
00:25:10,360 --> 00:25:12,613
他可是唯一一名海軍飛行員
You're looking at the only naval aviator on active duty

316
00:25:12,696 --> 00:25:14,197
曾在空戰擊落敵機
with a confirmed air-to-air kill.

317
00:25:14,281 --> 00:25:15,115
別說了
Stop.

318
00:25:15,198 --> 00:25:19,202
不過對方開的是韓戰時期的古董戰機
Mind you, the other guy was in
a museum piece from the Korean War.

319
00:25:19,286 --> 00:25:22,039
-冷戰
-不同的戰爭，同一個世紀
-Cold War.
-Different wars, same century.

320
00:25:22,122 --> 00:25:23,123
不是這個世紀
Not this one.

321
00:25:23,206 --> 00:25:24,583
妳朋友是誰？
Who are your friends?

322
00:25:24,666 --> 00:25:26,668
-復仇者
-粉弟
-Payback.
-Fanboy.

323
00:25:26,752 --> 00:25:28,754
-嘿，郊狼
-嘿
-Hey, Coyote.
-Hey.

324
00:25:28,837 --> 00:25:30,380
-他是誰？
-誰是誰？
-Who's he?
-Who's who?

325
00:25:33,467 --> 00:25:34,760
你幾時進來的？
When did you get in?

326
00:25:35,385 --> 00:25:37,471
我一直都在這裡
I've been here the whole time.

327
00:25:38,138 --> 00:25:40,182
-他開匿蹤戰機
-他能隱形
-The man's a stealth pilot.
-Literally.

328
00:25:40,265 --> 00:25:42,643
我是武器系統操作官
Weapons systems officer, actually.

329
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:44,728
毫無幽默感
With no sense of humor.

330
00:25:46,688 --> 00:25:47,856
他們叫你什麼？
What do they call you?

331
00:25:48,565 --> 00:25:49,900
巴布
Bob.

332
00:25:49,983 --> 00:25:51,234
你的呼號啦
No, your call sign.

333
00:25:54,154 --> 00:25:55,155
巴布
Bob.

334
00:25:55,656 --> 00:25:56,573
巴布佛洛伊德
Bob Floyd.

335
00:25:57,449 --> 00:26:00,285
你就是我新的武器官？
You're my new backseater? From Lemoore?

336
00:26:01,453 --> 00:26:03,163
看來是這樣，對啊
Looks like it. Yeah.

337
00:26:03,749 --> 00:26:06,186
♪ Bang a gong, get it on ♪

338
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:08,085
打一場撞球
Nine-ball, Bob.

339
00:26:08,835 --> 00:26:09,670
把球排好
Rack 'em.

340
00:26:11,672 --> 00:26:12,923
好吧
Okay.

341
00:26:13,590 --> 00:26:15,592
-親愛的潘妮
-是
-Penny, my dear.
-Yeah.

342
00:26:15,676 --> 00:26:17,844
再來四杯啤酒，老頭子請客
I'll have four more on the old-timer.

343
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:33,039
♪ And i'm the only son of a gun ♪

344
00:26:34,695 --> 00:26:36,196
布雷德蕭
Bradshaw!

345
00:26:36,947 --> 00:26:38,448
是你嗎？
Is that you?

346
00:26:44,079 --> 00:26:46,164
原來你回美國啦？
This is how I find out you're stateside?

347
00:26:46,290 --> 00:26:48,166
對啊，我想給妳個驚喜
Yeah, I just thought I'd surprise you.

348
00:26:50,961 --> 00:26:53,088
我也給你個驚喜
I guess I surprised you back.

349
00:26:54,798 --> 00:26:56,591
-見到妳真好
-我也是
-It's good to see you.
-Good to see you too.

350
00:26:59,303 --> 00:27:01,054
-來吧
-謝謝
-Here you go.
-Thank you.

351
00:27:01,138 --> 00:27:02,848
謝啦，老爹
Much appreciated, Pops.

352
00:27:10,314 --> 00:27:13,150
趁人少的時候幫我結帳吧
How about ringing me up before the evening rush?

353
00:27:27,289 --> 00:27:28,540
布雷德蕭
Bradshaw.

354
00:27:28,624 --> 00:27:30,208
沒想到你會來
As I live and breathe.

355
00:27:31,043 --> 00:27:32,044
劊子手
Hangman.

356
00:27:32,127 --> 00:27:34,296
你看起來…還不賴
You look… good.

357
00:27:35,464 --> 00:27:37,215
我是很厲害，公雞
Well, I am good, Rooster.

358
00:27:39,051 --> 00:27:40,052
我超厲害的
I'm very good.

359
00:27:40,636 --> 00:27:42,179
老實說
In fact,

360
00:27:42,262 --> 00:27:44,056
我厲害到沒人信
I am too good to be true.

361
00:27:44,139 --> 00:27:45,390
所以…
So,

362
00:27:45,474 --> 00:27:48,018
有人知道為什麼把我們找回來嗎？
anybody know what this special detachment is all about?

363
00:27:48,101 --> 00:27:51,146
任務就是任務，我不問為什麼
No, mission's a mission. They don't confront me.

364
00:27:51,897 --> 00:27:54,858
我只想知道，誰會是隊長？
What I want to know: Who's gonna be team leader?

365
00:27:55,567 --> 00:27:59,571
又有哪幾個夠資格跟我出任務？
And which one of y'all has what it takes to follow me?

366
00:28:01,073 --> 00:28:04,576
劊子手，跟你只會提早進棺材
Hangman, the only place you'll lead anyone is an early grave.

367
00:28:13,418 --> 00:28:17,172
跟你只會…耗盡燃油
Well, anyone who follows you is just gonna run out of fuel.

368
00:28:18,006 --> 00:28:20,300
你就像隻公雞，對吧？
But that's just you, ain't it, Rooster?

369
00:28:21,093 --> 00:28:23,595
只會窩在駕駛艙
You're snug on that perch,

370
00:28:23,679 --> 00:28:25,889
等著永遠都不會來的…
waiting for just the right moment…

371
00:28:28,016 --> 00:28:29,351
大好機會
that never comes.

372
00:28:29,938 --> 00:28:31,374
♪ Slow ride ♪

373
00:28:32,771 --> 00:28:34,690
我超愛這首歌
I love this song!

374
00:28:34,700 --> 00:28:36,075
♪ Slow ride ♪

375
00:28:37,728 --> 00:28:40,122
♪ take it easy ♪

376
00:28:41,822 --> 00:28:43,490
他一點都沒變
Well, he hasn't changed.

377
00:28:44,533 --> 00:28:46,702
是啊，還是老樣子
Nope. Sure hasn't.

378
00:28:46,716 --> 00:28:48,565
♪ Take it easy ♪

379
00:28:51,290 --> 00:28:52,332
你們看
Check it out.

380
00:28:53,417 --> 00:28:54,543
又來了一群
More patches.

381
00:28:55,085 --> 00:28:58,171
哈佛、耶魯、奧馬哈，靠，那是費茲
That's Harvard, Yale, Omaha. Shit, that's Fritz.

382
00:28:58,255 --> 00:29:00,465
這是什麼任務？
What the hell kind of mission is this?

383
00:29:01,466 --> 00:29:03,468
我們不該問這問題
That's not the question we should be asking.

384
00:29:04,261 --> 00:29:06,263
大家都是頂尖高手
Everyone here is the best there is.

385
00:29:07,764 --> 00:29:09,725
誰能當我們的教官？
Who the hell are they gonna get to teach us?

386
00:29:13,145 --> 00:29:14,688
信用卡刷不過
It's been declined.

387
00:29:15,272 --> 00:29:16,106
妳在開玩笑
You're kidding.

388
00:29:31,788 --> 00:29:34,041
大夥兒，來吧
Hey, guys. Come on.

389
00:29:48,138 --> 00:29:49,181
我不如付…
我不如付…
How about…

390
00:29:50,724 --> 00:29:52,476
那不夠
That won't cover it.

391
00:29:57,940 --> 00:30:00,442
我明天帶錢過來
I'll come by tomorrow and bring you the cash.

392
00:30:00,525 --> 00:30:03,403
規矩就是規矩，彼得
I'm afraid rules are rules, Pete.

393
00:30:09,493 --> 00:30:12,371
丟出去…丟出去…
Overboard! Overboard!

394
00:30:13,288 --> 00:30:14,539
真假？
Really?

395
00:30:15,582 --> 00:30:18,669
丟出去…丟出去…
Overboard! Overboard!

396
00:30:25,884 --> 00:30:27,761
見到你真好，彼得
Great to see you, Pete!

397
00:30:28,428 --> 00:30:31,264
Overboard! Overboard!

398
00:30:34,893 --> 00:30:37,271
多謝了，隨時再回來
♪ Thanks for the beers! Come back anytime!♪

399
00:30:48,907 --> 00:30:51,410
♪你讓我意亂神迷，神魂顛倒♪
♪ You shake my nerves And you rattle my brain♪

400
00:30:51,493 --> 00:30:54,371
♪太多的愛讓人精神錯亂♪
♪ Too much love drives a man insane♪

401
00:30:54,454 --> 00:30:57,124
♪你害我理智斷線，欣喜若狂♪
♪ You broke my will, but what a thrill♪

402
00:30:57,207 --> 00:31:00,419
♪愛就像一團大大的火球♪
♪ Goodness gracious, great balls of fire!♪

403
00:31:00,502 --> 00:31:03,171
♪我嘲笑愛情，以為那很可笑♪
♪ I laughed at love 'Cause I thought it was funny♪

404
00:31:03,255 --> 00:31:06,383
♪但你姍姍而來，打動我的心♪
♪ But you came along and you moved me, honey♪

405
00:31:06,466 --> 00:31:09,219
♪令我領悟到，愛情的美好♪
♪ I changed my mind, this love is fine♪

406
00:31:09,303 --> 00:31:12,055
♪愛就像是一團大大的火球♪
♪ Goodness gracious, great balls of fire!♪

407
00:31:12,139 --> 00:31:14,433
♪吻我吧，寶貝♪
♪ Kiss me, baby♪

408
00:31:20,022 --> 00:31:22,858
♪愛就像是一團大大的火球♪
♪ Goodness gracious, great balls of fire!♪

409
00:31:39,333 --> 00:31:42,419
高度八千英呎…七千英呎
Altitude 8,000… 7,000…

410
00:31:42,502 --> 00:31:44,838
呆頭鵝，我抓不到彈射手把
Goose, I can't reach the ejection handle.

411
00:31:44,921 --> 00:31:46,923
彈射…彈射…
Eject, eject, eject!

412
00:31:52,846 --> 00:31:54,348
呆頭鵝！不！
Goose! Oh, no!

413
00:31:54,431 --> 00:31:57,225
他真的很愛跟你飛行，獨行俠
God, he loved flying with you, Maverick.

414
00:32:32,224 --> 00:32:34,661
♪ Come on, baby you're driving me crazy ♪

415
00:32:34,835 --> 00:32:37,925
♪ goodness gracious great balls of fire! ♪

416
00:32:41,311 --> 00:32:42,521
立正！
Attention on deck!

417
00:32:53,448 --> 00:32:54,491
早安
Morning.

418
00:32:55,158 --> 00:32:57,327
歡迎參加特訓營
Welcome to your special training detachment.

419
00:32:57,411 --> 00:32:58,453
坐下來
Be seated.

420
00:32:59,037 --> 00:33:01,707
我是貝茲少將，航空作戰中心指揮官
I'm Admiral Bates, NAWDC commander.

421
00:33:01,790 --> 00:33:03,542
你們都是捍衛小組畢業生
You're all TOPGUN graduates.

422
00:33:04,334 --> 00:33:05,627
頂尖飛行員
The elite.

423
00:33:05,711 --> 00:33:07,713
菁英中的菁英
The best of the best.

424
00:33:08,297 --> 00:33:10,132
那是過去式
That was yesterday.

425
00:33:11,174 --> 00:33:15,178
敵人全新的第五代戰機趕上我們
The enemy's new fifth-generation fighter
has leveled the playing field.

426
00:33:15,262 --> 00:33:16,888
細節不多，但要知道
Details are few, but you can be sure

427
00:33:16,972 --> 00:33:19,016
我們不再擁有科技的優勢
we no longer possess the technological advantage.

428
00:33:19,099 --> 00:33:22,394
獲勝的關鍵
Success, now more than ever,

429
00:33:22,477 --> 00:33:25,647
取決於駕駛艙內的男女飛行員
comes down to the man or woman in the box.

430
00:33:26,565 --> 00:33:28,859
你們有一半會入選
Half of you will make the cut.

431
00:33:28,942 --> 00:33:30,819
其中一個會是任務隊長
One of you will be named mission leader.

432
00:33:31,570 --> 00:33:34,072
另一半則是儲備飛官
The other half will remain in reserve.

433
00:33:35,073 --> 00:33:37,075
你們的教官是你們的學長
Your instructor is a TOPGUN graduate

434
00:33:37,159 --> 00:33:39,703
他擁有你們必須掌握這次任務的
with real-world experience in every mission aspect

435
00:33:39,786 --> 00:33:41,371
實戰經驗技巧
you will be expected to master.

436
00:33:42,331 --> 00:33:44,541
他的豐功偉業是傳奇事蹟
His exploits are legendary.

437
00:33:46,001 --> 00:33:48,170
而且是這項計畫有史以來
And he's considered to be one of the finest pilots

438
00:33:48,253 --> 00:33:50,255
訓練出來最優秀的飛行員
this program has ever produced.

439
00:33:51,673 --> 00:33:53,258
他能夠教導你們的
What he has to teach you

440
00:33:53,342 --> 00:33:56,720
極可能會關乎你們的生死
may very well mean the difference between life and death.

441
00:33:57,554 --> 00:33:59,890
容我介紹彼得米契爾上校
I give you Captain Pete Mitchell.

442
00:34:00,390 --> 00:34:03,185
呼號是獨行俠
Call sign: "Maverick."

443
00:34:07,731 --> 00:34:08,732
早安
Good morning.

444
00:34:17,114 --> 00:34:18,784
F-18戰機訓練及標準操作程序
The F-18 NATOPS.

445
00:34:20,368 --> 00:34:23,872
包含了你們應該知道的一切
It contains everything they want you
to know about your aircraft.

446
00:34:24,873 --> 00:34:27,668
我猜你們都背得滾瓜爛熟
I'm assuming you know the book inside and out.

447
00:34:27,750 --> 00:34:29,002
-沒錯
-一定要的
-Damn right.
-Damn straight.

448
00:34:29,085 --> 00:34:30,252
你說得對
You got it.

449
00:34:38,303 --> 00:34:39,805
敵人也都知道
So does your enemy.

450
00:34:40,389 --> 00:34:41,890
他又來了
And we're off.

451
00:34:42,933 --> 00:34:46,143
敵人不知道的…是你們的極限
But what the enemy doesn't know is your limits.

452
00:34:46,937 --> 00:34:48,647
我打算找到它們
I intend to find them,

453
00:34:48,730 --> 00:34:50,357
測試它們
test them,

454
00:34:50,941 --> 00:34:52,317
逼你們超越極限
push beyond.

455
00:34:53,485 --> 00:34:57,072
今天就先從…你們自以為知道的開始
Today we'll start with what you only think you know.

456
00:34:58,991 --> 00:35:00,784
讓我看看你們的能耐
You show me what you're made of.

457
00:35:05,914 --> 00:35:06,915
公雞
Rooster.

458
00:35:08,083 --> 00:35:09,126
布雷德利
Bradley.

459
00:35:09,751 --> 00:35:11,503
布雷德蕭中尉
Lieutenant Bradshaw!

460
00:35:13,505 --> 00:35:14,506
是，長官
Yes, sir.

461
00:35:15,507 --> 00:35:17,217
我們之間沒必要這樣
Let's not do it like this.

462
00:35:18,010 --> 00:35:19,386
你會把我刷下來嗎？
You gonna wash me out?

463
00:35:21,013 --> 00:35:22,723
那要看你，不是看我
That'll be up to you, not me.

464
00:35:25,017 --> 00:35:26,393
我可以走了嗎？
Am I dismissed?

465
00:35:43,952 --> 00:35:46,371
早安，飛行員，我是你們的上校
Good morning, aviators. This is your captain speaking.

466
00:35:46,455 --> 00:35:48,582
歡迎參加基本飛行訓練
Welcome to basic fighter maneuvers.

467
00:35:50,125 --> 00:35:53,086
今天要演練空中纏鬥
As briefed, today's exercise is dogfighting.

468
00:35:53,170 --> 00:35:54,796
只用機關槍，不用飛彈
Guns only, no missiles.

469
00:35:55,797 --> 00:35:58,925
限低不能低於五千呎
We do not go below the hard deck of 5,000 feet.

470
00:35:59,009 --> 00:36:01,928
兩架戰機一組，將我擊落，否則…
Working as a team, you have to shoot me down, or else.

471
00:36:02,012 --> 00:36:05,349
-否則怎樣？
-我會反擊
-Or else what, sir?
-Or else I shoot back.

472
00:36:05,432 --> 00:36:08,352
只要擊落一架戰機，兩架都算輸
If I shoot either one of you down, you both lose.

473
00:36:08,435 --> 00:36:10,312
這傢伙太臭屁了
This guy needs an ego check.

474
00:36:10,395 --> 00:36:11,730
我們會讓他吃癟
We'll see to that.

475
00:36:11,813 --> 00:36:14,483
-不如來賭一把
-你想賭什麼？
-What say we put some skin in the game?
-What do you have in mind?

476
00:36:14,566 --> 00:36:17,444
先被擊落做兩百下伏地挺身
Whoever gets shot down first has to do 200 push-ups.

477
00:36:17,527 --> 00:36:20,280
大夥兒，很多下耶
Guys. That's a lot of push-ups.

478
00:36:20,364 --> 00:36:22,491
訓練不是叫假的，長官
They don't call it an exercise for nothing, sir.

479
00:36:22,574 --> 00:36:24,493
那就一言為定
You got yourself a deal, gentlemen.

480
00:36:24,576 --> 00:36:26,870
開戰了，拼了啦
Fight's on. Let's turn and burn.

481
00:36:28,455 --> 00:36:29,706
粉弟，看到他嗎？
Fanboy, you see him?

482
00:36:29,790 --> 00:36:32,793
他不在前方，一定在後面
Nothing on radar up ahead. He must be somewhere behind us.

483
00:36:35,420 --> 00:36:37,047
-可惡
-搞什麼？
-Damn it!
-What the hell?

484
00:36:37,130 --> 00:36:37,965
該死！
Shit!

485
00:36:40,036 --> 00:36:42,212
♪ We Don't get fooled again ♪

486
00:36:42,678 --> 00:36:43,512
別這麼衝，獨行俠
Easy, Maverick.

487
00:36:43,595 --> 00:36:46,682
別在第一天就被炒魷魚
Let's try not to get fired on the first day.

488
00:36:46,765 --> 00:36:49,685
看見目標…獨行俠逼近，向左急轉
Tally, tally, tally! Maverick's coming in! Break left!

489
00:36:49,768 --> 00:36:50,936
向左急轉
Breaking left.

490
00:36:52,938 --> 00:36:54,982
復仇者，你的僚機呢？
Payback, where's your wingman?

491
00:36:55,065 --> 00:36:57,276
-公雞，你在哪？
-我會罩你
-Rooster, where are you?
-I got your back.

492
00:36:57,359 --> 00:36:59,861
我來了，撐著點，撐著點
I'm coming. Hang in there. Hang in there.

493
00:36:59,945 --> 00:37:01,280
快點，兄弟！快點
Hurry up, man! Hurry up!

494
00:37:05,033 --> 00:37:06,994
-復仇者，向右急轉
-向右急轉
-Payback, break right.
-Breaking right.

495
00:37:08,370 --> 00:37:11,790
公雞救了你們，但他會付出代價
Rooster just saved your life, fellas. But it's gonna cost him.

496
00:37:11,873 --> 00:37:13,542
這次不會，老頭
Not this time, old man.

497
00:37:16,211 --> 00:37:17,838
別被他激怒，獨行俠
Don't let him get to you, Maverick.

498
00:37:20,599 --> 00:37:24,690
♪ Smile and grin at the change all around pick up my guitar... ♪

499
00:37:24,803 --> 00:37:27,431
公雞，你飛得太低，快爬升 你快到限低了
Rooster, you're too low! Pull up! You're hitting the hard deck!

500
00:37:27,514 --> 00:37:30,017
-高度，高度
-慘了
-Altitude. Altitude.
-Oh, shit.

501
00:37:31,436 --> 00:37:33,655
♪ Get on my knees and pray ♪

502
00:37:34,438 --> 00:37:35,439
你被擊落了
That's a kill.

503
00:37:35,522 --> 00:37:37,899
伏低，109下
Down! 109.

504
00:37:38,859 --> 00:37:41,486
伏低，110下
Down! 110.

505
00:37:43,405 --> 00:37:45,157
那應該是我們
That should be us down there.

506
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:46,366
但並不是
But it's not.

507
00:37:47,159 --> 00:37:49,661
現在你們也知道公雞會犧牲自己
And now you know a little something about Rooster.

508
00:37:51,663 --> 00:37:53,790
留守在跑道，等我們回來
Hold that tarmac down till we get back, brother, all right?

509
00:37:53,874 --> 00:37:55,584
拍一張，大夥兒
Get in there, boys.

510
00:37:58,712 --> 00:38:00,464
-你被擊落了
-靠
-That's a kill.
-Damn!

511
00:38:01,214 --> 00:38:02,799
-你死了
-可惡
-Smoked.
-Damn it.

512
00:38:03,508 --> 00:38:06,136
剛才自拍得很爽嘛，伏低
It was all fun and games in that selfie, wasn't it? Down!

513
00:38:06,219 --> 00:38:07,054
嘿，鳳凰
Say, Phoenix.

514
00:38:07,137 --> 00:38:09,973
不如告訴大家“巴布”是別的小名
How's about we tell everybody "Bob" stands for something?

515
00:38:10,057 --> 00:38:12,392
-不只是羅勃特
-別上當
-Other than Robert, I mean.
-Don't take the bait, Bob.

516
00:38:12,476 --> 00:38:14,519
想知道他為什麼叫劊子手嗎？
Want to know why we call him Hangman?

517
00:38:14,603 --> 00:38:16,855
我想到了，“巴布叭噗”
I got it. "Baby On Board."

518
00:38:19,274 --> 00:38:20,734
靠！
Shit!

519
00:38:22,027 --> 00:38:23,946
各位飛官好，開戰了
Greetings, aviators. Fight's on.

520
00:38:24,571 --> 00:38:26,823
鳳凰，把這傢伙擊落
All right, Phoenix, let's take this guy out!

521
00:38:26,907 --> 00:38:28,075
小心後方，鳳凰
Watch your back, Phoenix.

522
00:38:28,158 --> 00:38:30,035
-向右急轉
-Break right!
-Breaking right.

523
00:38:32,454 --> 00:38:33,455
他去哪兒？
Where's he going?

524
00:38:33,538 --> 00:38:36,625
他是劊子手，只會害死你
That's why we call him Hangman.
He'll always hang you out to dry.

525
00:38:37,626 --> 00:38:39,127
丟下你的僚機
Leaving your wingman.

526
00:38:39,211 --> 00:38:40,879
很久沒看過這一招了
There's a strategy I haven't seen in a while.

527
00:38:40,963 --> 00:38:43,382
他在笑妳，妳忍得了嗎？
He called you a man, Phoenix. You gonna take that?

528
00:38:43,465 --> 00:38:44,883
只要他噹你就忍得了
So long as he doesn't call you a man.

529
00:38:44,967 --> 00:38:46,927
巴布，獨行俠在哪？
Talk to me, Bob. Where's Maverick?

530
00:38:47,010 --> 00:38:49,012
天啊，他已經繞回來了！
Jesus, his nose is already coming around!

531
00:38:49,096 --> 00:38:50,472
幫我甩掉他，劊子手
Get him off me, Hangman!

532
00:38:50,555 --> 00:38:54,518
各位聽眾，我要埋了這化石
For all you folks at home, this is how you bury a fossil.

533
00:38:54,601 --> 00:38:57,229
劊子手，該教訓你了
All right, Hangman. Time to teach you a lesson.

534
00:38:57,312 --> 00:38:59,189
-妳掛了，鳳凰
-混蛋
-You're out, Phoenix.
-Son of a bitch!

535
00:39:00,482 --> 00:39:01,483
開戰了
That's it.

536
00:39:01,566 --> 00:39:04,069
-來吧，獨行俠，看你有多厲害
-來追我啊
-Let's go, Mav. Let's see what you got.
-Come get me.

537
00:39:06,488 --> 00:39:08,198
惡魔散退，劊子手來也
Evil be gone. Hangman's coming.

538
00:39:09,408 --> 00:39:11,618
我得承認，你很行
Yeah, you're good. I'll give you that.

539
00:39:13,668 --> 00:39:16,323
♪ Meet the new boss ♪

540
00:39:18,125 --> 00:39:21,378
靠，看不到他，我離他多近？
Shit. Phoenix, I can't see him. How close am I?

541
00:39:21,461 --> 00:39:23,839
-鳳凰？
-我掛了，豬頭
-Phoenix?
-I'm dead, dickhead.

542
00:39:23,922 --> 00:39:25,799
下輩子再見，捕手
See you in the afterlife, Bagman.

543
00:39:27,217 --> 00:39:28,802
他在哪？他在哪？
Where is he? Where is he?

544
00:39:29,511 --> 00:39:30,804
你死了
That's a kill.

545
00:39:31,513 --> 00:39:35,100
79，伏低，80，伏低
Seventy-nine. Down. Eighty. Down.

546
00:39:35,183 --> 00:39:36,351
開戰吧，下一個是誰？
Let's go. Who's next?

547
00:39:37,603 --> 00:39:39,354
-擊中你了，奧馬哈
-可惡
-I got you, Omaha.
-Damn it!

548
00:39:42,399 --> 00:39:44,651
-你死了，郊狼
-收到
-Lights out, Coyote.
-Copy kill.

549
00:39:44,735 --> 00:39:49,197
伏低，51，伏低，52
Down. Fifty-one. Down. Fifty-two.

550
00:39:52,034 --> 00:39:55,037
公雞，能問個私人問題嗎？
So, Rooster, mind if I ask you a personal question?

551
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:56,413
我能說不能嗎？
Would it matter if I did?

552
00:39:56,496 --> 00:39:58,749
你和獨行俠有什麼過節？
What's the story with you and Maverick?

553
00:39:58,832 --> 00:40:01,877
-你好像跟他過不去
-不關你的事
-It seems like he's got you rattled.
-That's none of your business.

554
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:03,795
他到底在哪裡？
Now where the hell is he?

555
00:40:03,879 --> 00:40:05,547
一直都在這裡
Been here the whole time.

556
00:40:06,632 --> 00:40:08,467
哇哩咧
Holy shit.

557
00:40:10,552 --> 00:40:11,720
看到我了嗎？
You see me now?

558
00:40:12,638 --> 00:40:14,431
來吧，速戰速決
Come on, let's get it over with.

559
00:40:15,057 --> 00:40:16,475
開戰了
Fight's on!

560
00:40:18,185 --> 00:40:20,520
那兩個人到底是怎麼回事？
What is with these two?

561
00:40:25,067 --> 00:40:28,528
你逼我們盤旋俯衝，要怎麼解套？
All right, you put us here. How you gonna get yourself out?

562
00:40:29,112 --> 00:40:31,198
你隨時都能撤
You can bail out anytime.

563
00:40:31,281 --> 00:40:32,616
公雞，你想俯衝到多低？
How low you want to go, Rooster?

564
00:40:32,699 --> 00:40:35,953
比你更低，你懂我意思
I can go as low as you, sir! And that's saying something.

565
00:40:39,790 --> 00:40:41,792
過去的就讓它過去
What's past is past. For both of us.

566
00:40:41,875 --> 00:40:43,710
你很想，對吧？
You'd like to believe that, wouldn't you?

567
00:40:43,794 --> 00:40:46,880
限低是五千呎，就快到了
Hard deck is 5,000 feet, fellas. You are running out of room.

568
00:40:47,881 --> 00:40:48,882
高度
Altitude.

569
00:40:48,966 --> 00:40:50,968
你打算害我們都墜機
Your strategy is about to run us into the ground.

570
00:40:51,051 --> 00:40:53,512
-你想怎樣？
-高度…
-What's your move?
-Altitude. Altitude.

571
00:40:53,595 --> 00:40:54,972
高度
Altitude.

572
00:40:56,765 --> 00:40:59,643
高度…高度…
Altitude. Altitude. Altitude.

573
00:40:59,726 --> 00:41:02,145
高度，高度
Altitude. Altitude.

574
00:41:04,189 --> 00:41:06,858
爬升…爬升…
Pull up! Pull up! Pull up! Pull up!

575
00:41:07,567 --> 00:41:08,568
爬升…爬升…
Pull up! Pull up!

576
00:41:11,822 --> 00:41:13,532
你行的，別猶豫，放手去做
You got it. Don't think, just do.

577
00:41:14,700 --> 00:41:17,244
你逮到他了，飛低然後射擊
Come on, Rooster, you got him! Drop down and take the shot!

578
00:41:18,870 --> 00:41:19,788
太低了
It's too low.

579
00:41:20,831 --> 00:41:22,541
太遲了，你錯過機會
Too late. You had your chance.

580
00:41:28,672 --> 00:41:31,425
你被擊落，玩完了
That's a kill. Knock it off.

581
00:41:32,426 --> 00:41:33,552
可惡
Damn it!

582
00:41:33,635 --> 00:41:35,512
還是老樣子
Same old Rooster.

583
00:41:38,056 --> 00:41:40,392
去找宏多做伏地挺身
Go see Hondo about your push-ups.

584
00:41:48,609 --> 00:41:50,110
好了，夠了
All right, that's enough.

585
00:41:50,777 --> 00:41:52,863
公雞，夠了
Rooster. That's enough, man.

586
00:42:07,252 --> 00:42:10,922
違紀抗命，你想被踢走嗎？
Breaking the hard deck, insubordination.
Are you trying to get kicked out?

587
00:42:11,006 --> 00:42:12,466
別擔心
Don't worry about it.

588
00:42:12,966 --> 00:42:15,469
我想要出這項任務
Look, I'm going on this mission.

589
00:42:16,428 --> 00:42:19,222
但你被踢走，我就得和劊子手合作
But if you get kicked out, you leave us flying with Hangman.

590
00:42:19,848 --> 00:42:23,477
-那是怎麼回事？
-他拿掉我的文件
-Talk to me. What the hell was that?
-He pulled my papers.

591
00:42:23,560 --> 00:42:27,022
-什麼？誰？
-獨行俠
-What? Who?
-Maverick.

592
00:42:28,190 --> 00:42:30,734
他拿掉我海軍官校的申請書
He pulled my application to the Naval Academy.

593
00:42:31,818 --> 00:42:33,820
害我浪費了四年
Set me back four years.

594
00:42:36,323 --> 00:42:37,783
他為什麼要這麼做？
Why would he do that?

595
00:42:43,622 --> 00:42:46,166
限低是五千呎
The hard deck is 5,000 feet above ground level.

596
00:42:46,249 --> 00:42:48,585
不只是為了飛行員的安全
A parameter is set not just for the safety of our pilots,

597
00:42:48,669 --> 00:42:50,170
也是為了戰機的安全
but for the safety of their aircraft.

598
00:42:50,253 --> 00:42:54,466
五千呎不只是規定，更是一條鐵律
5,000 feet is not just a rule.
It is a law, as immutable as gravity.

599
00:42:54,549 --> 00:42:57,219
這項任務的限低會更低
The hard deck will be much lower for the mission, sir.

600
00:42:57,302 --> 00:43:00,430
沒我的允許不准更改
And it will not change without my approval!

601
00:43:00,514 --> 00:43:02,432
尤其是在演練空戰的時候
Especially not in the middle of an exercise.

602
00:43:03,100 --> 00:43:06,478
你那招眼鏡蛇機動會害死你們三個
And that Cobra maneuver of yours?
That could've got all three of you killed.

603
00:43:06,561 --> 00:43:08,438
我不想再看到那種屁事
I never want to see that shit again.

604
00:43:09,523 --> 00:43:11,775
你以為你在教什麼？
What exactly do you suppose you were teaching, Captain?

605
00:43:11,858 --> 00:43:14,278
他們雖然很優秀，但還有得要學
That as good as they are, sir,
they still have something to learn.

606
00:43:14,361 --> 00:43:16,947
他們是世上最頂尖的飛行員
You are talking about the best
fighter pilots on the planet, Captain.

607
00:43:17,030 --> 00:43:18,782
他們一直都被吹捧
And they've been told that their entire career,

608
00:43:18,865 --> 00:43:20,742
卻只會從高空投擲炸彈
while they've been dropping bombs from a high altitude

609
00:43:20,826 --> 00:43:22,577
沒有空戰的經驗
with little to no dogfighting.

610
00:43:22,661 --> 00:43:25,414
這是他們從來沒有執行過的任務
The parameters of this mission call for
something they have never encountered.

611
00:43:25,497 --> 00:43:29,209
你只有不到三週要教會他們團隊合作
Okay, you have less than three weeks
to teach them how to fight as a team

612
00:43:30,043 --> 00:43:31,336
還有擊中目標
and how to strike the target.

613
00:43:31,420 --> 00:43:33,171
也要活著回來
And how to come home.

614
00:43:36,008 --> 00:43:38,010
必須活著回來，長官
And how to come home, sir.

615
00:43:43,682 --> 00:43:45,350
每項任務都有風險
Every mission has its risks.

616
00:43:46,226 --> 00:43:48,103
這些飛行員都能接受
These pilots accept that.

617
00:43:48,186 --> 00:43:49,771
我不接受，長官
I don't, sir.

618
00:43:53,984 --> 00:43:55,319
從今天起，每天早上
Every morning, from this day forward,

619
00:43:55,402 --> 00:43:58,113
你要書面報告你的教戰計畫
you will brief us on your instructional plans in writing.

620
00:43:58,196 --> 00:44:01,116
沒有我的允許不准做出更動
And nothing will change without my express approval.

621
00:44:01,199 --> 00:44:04,369
-包括限低？
-尤其是限低，上校
-Including the hard deck, sir?
-Especially the hard deck, Captain.

622
00:44:06,455 --> 00:44:07,539
長官
Sir.

623
00:44:08,457 --> 00:44:09,666
這是什麼？
What is this?

624
00:44:09,750 --> 00:44:11,418
要求降低限低，長官
It's a request to lower the hard deck, sir,

625
00:44:11,501 --> 00:44:13,920
為了演練低空轟炸任務
to practice a low-level bombing run per the mission parameters.

626
00:44:20,010 --> 00:44:22,638
有關時機的掌控要多注意點，上校
You could learn a thing or two about timing, Captain.

627
00:44:23,472 --> 00:44:24,431
唷，郊狼
Yo, Coyote.

628
00:44:25,140 --> 00:44:26,433
你看看
Take a look at this.

629
00:44:30,354 --> 00:44:33,065
傳奇人物，就是他
The man, the legend. There he is.

630
00:44:33,148 --> 00:44:35,150
不是啦，他旁邊那個
No, no, no. Next to him.

631
00:44:36,109 --> 00:44:38,153
很眼熟吧？
He look familiar to you?

632
00:44:40,072 --> 00:44:41,698
這什麼情況？
What have we here?

633
00:44:42,491 --> 00:44:44,201
布雷德蕭
Bradshaw.

634
00:44:45,160 --> 00:44:46,828
我不敢相信
As I live and breathe.

635
00:44:50,040 --> 00:44:52,584
弟歐…你長大了
Hey, Theo, you got big.

636
00:44:53,418 --> 00:44:54,544
嘿，獨行俠
Hey, Mav.

637
00:45:01,635 --> 00:45:02,678
艾蜜莉雅？
Amelia?

638
00:45:02,761 --> 00:45:04,304
我知道，我長大了
I know. I got big.

639
00:45:04,388 --> 00:45:05,639
是啊
Yes.

640
00:45:06,723 --> 00:45:08,016
酒吧五點才開
Bar opens at 5:00.

641
00:45:08,850 --> 00:45:10,852
我只是來還錢的
No, I just came by to pay off a debt.

642
00:45:10,936 --> 00:45:12,187
媽！
Mom!

643
00:45:16,900 --> 00:45:19,861
-妳爸好嗎？
-跟他老婆在夏威夷
-Hey, how's your dad?
-With his wife, in Hawaii.

644
00:45:19,945 --> 00:45:21,321
媽！
Mom!

645
00:45:22,281 --> 00:45:24,408
獨行俠說他欠妳錢
Mav says he owes you money.

646
00:45:25,909 --> 00:45:27,911
-沒關係啦
-我堅持
-Don't worry about it.
-I insist.

647
00:45:31,123 --> 00:45:34,793
謝了，上校，酒帳還清了
Thank you, Captain. Consider your tab closed.

648
00:45:35,794 --> 00:45:37,671
還是上校？
Captain? Still?

649
00:45:38,297 --> 00:45:40,424
戰功彪炳的上校
A highly decorated captain.

650
00:45:40,507 --> 00:45:41,550
做完功課
Finish up.

651
00:45:41,633 --> 00:45:43,427
得把帆船開到船塢
We have to get the boat to the yard.

652
00:45:43,510 --> 00:45:45,470
-我不行
-什麼意思？
-I can't go.
-What do you mean, you can't go?

653
00:45:45,554 --> 00:45:48,890
明天要抽考，我得用功唸書
他們今天才通知我們
Test tomorrow. I have to study. They only told us today.

654
00:45:48,974 --> 00:45:50,934
我不能一個人駕船
Well, I can't sail her alone.

655
00:45:51,018 --> 00:45:52,436
用引擎啊
Just use the engine.

656
00:45:52,519 --> 00:45:54,688
為什麼要開到船塢？
Why are we taking her to the yard?

657
00:45:55,314 --> 00:45:56,773
修理引擎
To fix the engine.

658
00:45:57,566 --> 00:45:58,567
我能幫忙
I can help.

659
00:46:04,823 --> 00:46:08,035
-浪比我預期的更大
-還用說
-Little rougher than I was expecting.
-You don't say.

660
00:46:08,744 --> 00:46:11,705
拉住控帆索，減低風力
Pull on the backstay. We'll de-power the sails.

661
00:46:11,788 --> 00:46:12,789
好啊
Okay.

662
00:46:13,332 --> 00:46:14,916
那什麼意思？
What does that mean?

663
00:46:16,335 --> 00:46:18,587
你是海軍耶
You're supposed to be in the navy!

664
00:46:18,670 --> 00:46:22,007
我不會航船，只會降落在航母
I don't sail boats, Penny. I land on them.

665
00:46:22,549 --> 00:46:25,761
這就像打開襟翼一樣
It's sort of like raising the flaps on an airplane.

666
00:46:25,844 --> 00:46:27,304
我要怎麼做？
So how do I do that?

667
00:46:28,055 --> 00:46:30,265
拉住那條綠繩索
You pull on that green line up there.

668
00:46:30,349 --> 00:46:31,683
綠繩索
Green line.

669
00:46:34,227 --> 00:46:35,771
對，用力拉
Yep. Pull it hard.

670
00:46:35,854 --> 00:46:38,774
很好，用力轉那個曲柄
Yep. Crank that winch right there,

671
00:46:38,857 --> 00:46:40,651
拉緊三角帆
tighten the jib.

672
00:46:41,360 --> 00:46:43,695
-用力轉，還行嗎？
-行
-Crank it. You okay?
-Yeah.

673
00:46:45,238 --> 00:46:46,198
很好
Good.

674
00:46:47,449 --> 00:46:48,450
現在…
Now,

675
00:46:49,868 --> 00:46:51,286
準備好了嗎？
you ready?

676
00:46:53,205 --> 00:46:54,289
準備好什麼？
For what?

677
00:46:54,873 --> 00:46:56,416
拉起風帆
The afterburner.

678
00:47:16,728 --> 00:47:18,563
現在你才算是海軍
Now you're in the navy.

679
00:47:40,836 --> 00:47:42,671
今天謝謝你幫忙
Thanks for helping out today.

680
00:47:44,381 --> 00:47:45,799
我好像沒幫到什麼
I'm not exactly sure I helped.

681
00:47:51,263 --> 00:47:52,764
別那副表情
Don't give me that look.

682
00:47:52,848 --> 00:47:54,182
什麼表情？
What look?

683
00:47:54,266 --> 00:47:55,892
那副表情
That one.

684
00:47:59,187 --> 00:48:00,480
晚安，彼得
Good night, Pete.

685
00:48:01,273 --> 00:48:02,608
晚安，潘妮
Night, Penny.

686
00:48:18,081 --> 00:48:19,583
媽，是妳嗎？
Mom, is that you?

687
00:48:20,208 --> 00:48:21,501
對啊
Yeah, it's me.

688
00:48:22,502 --> 00:48:24,212
我替妳做晚飯
I'll make you dinner.

689
00:48:24,296 --> 00:48:25,297
Okay.

690
00:48:26,965 --> 00:48:29,885
（抵達目標時間：三分鐘）

691
00:48:31,511 --> 00:48:33,764
時間…是最大的敵人
Time is your greatest enemy.

692
00:48:35,182 --> 00:48:37,309
任務第一階段是低空進入
Phase one of the mission will be a low-level ingress

693
00:48:37,392 --> 00:48:39,144
兩架戰機一組進行攻擊
attacking in two-plane teams.

694
00:48:39,728 --> 00:48:41,939
沿著狹窄的峽谷飛至目標
You'll fly along this narrow canyon to your target.

695
00:48:42,022 --> 00:48:45,442
雷達導引地對空飛彈防衛該地區
Radar-guided surface-to-air missiles defend the area.

696
00:48:45,525 --> 00:48:47,778
這些飛彈…極度致命
These SAMs, they're lethal.

697
00:48:48,445 --> 00:48:52,324
但它們負責防禦領空，不是峽谷
But they were designed to protect
the skies above, not the canyon below.

698
00:48:52,407 --> 00:48:56,286
因為敵人知道沒人會瘋狂到飛進峽谷
That's because the enemy knows no one is
insane enough to try and fly below them.

699
00:48:57,204 --> 00:48:59,164
我就是要訓練你們這麼做
That's exactly what I'm gonna train you to do.

700
00:49:00,207 --> 00:49:04,419
任務當天的飛行高度最多100呎
On the day, your altitude will be 100 feet maximum.

701
00:49:04,503 --> 00:49:07,631
超過這高度就會被雷達偵測…
You exceed this altitude, radar will spot you,

702
00:49:08,507 --> 00:49:10,008
你就死定了
and you're dead.

703
00:49:11,134 --> 00:49:13,095
飛行速度是660節…
Your airspeed will be 660 knots

704
00:49:13,929 --> 00:49:15,180
最低速度
minimum.

705
00:49:15,263 --> 00:49:17,599
抵達目標時間是兩分半鐘
Time to target: two and a half minutes.

706
00:49:18,183 --> 00:49:21,937
因為第五代戰機在附近軍用機場待命
That's because fifth-generation fighters
wait at an air base nearby.

707
00:49:22,813 --> 00:49:27,234
F-18戰機對上它們…必死無疑
In a head-to-head with these planes in your F-18s, you're dead.

708
00:49:27,985 --> 00:49:30,946
你們得飛進峽谷，擊中目標
That's why you need to get in, hit your target and be gone

709
00:49:31,029 --> 00:49:34,199
趁那些戰機尚未抵達時飛離敵區
before these planes even have a chance of catching you.

710
00:49:34,283 --> 00:49:37,119
時間就變得至關重要
This makes time your greatest adversary.

711
00:49:38,954 --> 00:49:42,249
你們要照著模擬峽谷的航道飛行
You'll fly a route in your nav system
that simulates the canyon.

712
00:49:43,041 --> 00:49:44,710
越快飛過峽谷
The faster you navigate this canyon,

713
00:49:44,793 --> 00:49:47,462
越不會被敵軍雷達偵測
the harder it'll be to stay
under the radar of these enemy SAMs.

714
00:49:48,463 --> 00:49:49,589
彎度越窄
The tighter the turns,

715
00:49:49,673 --> 00:49:52,884
身體承受的G力就越大
the more intensely the force of gravity
on your body multiplies,

716
00:49:53,552 --> 00:49:55,304
肺部受到擠壓
compressing your lungs,

717
00:49:55,387 --> 00:49:56,805
血液離開大腦
forcing the blood from your brain,

718
00:49:56,888 --> 00:50:00,100
減低判斷及反應時間
impairing your judgment and reaction time.

719
00:50:00,183 --> 00:50:02,561
今天的訓練比較輕鬆
So for today's lesson, we're gonna take it easy on you.

720
00:50:02,644 --> 00:50:05,647
高度三百呎，目標時間三分鐘
Max ceiling: 300 feet. Time to target: three minutes.

721
00:50:07,524 --> 00:50:08,734
祝好運
Good luck.

722
00:50:17,159 --> 00:50:18,952
目標時間一分半鐘
Time to target is one minute 30.

723
00:50:19,036 --> 00:50:21,455
我們落後兩秒，加速到480節
We are two seconds behind. Increase to 480 knots.

724
00:50:21,538 --> 00:50:22,789
我們得快點，郊狼
We got to move, Coyote.

725
00:50:23,665 --> 00:50:25,334
收到，加速中
Copy. Increasing speed.

726
00:50:27,711 --> 00:50:28,629
噢，靠
Oh, shit!

727
00:50:32,424 --> 00:50:33,467
他們怎麼會死？
Why are they dead?

728
00:50:33,550 --> 00:50:36,345
我們超過300呎
一枚地對空飛彈擊落我們
We broke the 300-foot ceiling, and a SAM took us out.

729
00:50:36,428 --> 00:50:38,055
不對，他們怎麼會死？
No. Why are they dead?

730
00:50:38,138 --> 00:50:40,474
我減速卻沒警告她，是我的錯
I slowed down and didn't give her
a warning. It was my fault.

731
00:50:40,557 --> 00:50:42,392
你為什麼沒警告隊友？
Was there a reason you didn't communicate with your team?

732
00:50:42,476 --> 00:50:43,602
我正在專心…
I was focusing on--

733
00:50:43,685 --> 00:50:45,479
說出家屬在葬禮能接受的理由
One that their family will accept at the funeral.

734
00:50:46,480 --> 00:50:47,439
我沒有，長官
None, sir.

735
00:50:48,398 --> 00:50:51,443
妳熟知地形，怎麼不知道要急轉？
Why didn't you anticipate the turn?
You were briefed on the terrain.

736
00:50:52,069 --> 00:50:54,780
別告訴我，告訴他的家屬
Don't tell me. Tell it to his family.

737
00:51:00,202 --> 00:51:02,746
劊子手，慢點，峽谷越來越窄
Hangman, ease up. The canyon's getting tighter.

738
00:51:02,829 --> 00:51:05,415
不行，復仇者，你要加速
Negative, Payback. Increase your speed.

739
00:51:07,042 --> 00:51:10,379
-你飛得太快
-提早達標是好事
-You're going too fast, man.
-No harm in being ahead of schedule.

740
00:51:12,589 --> 00:51:15,550
快減速，我無法留在航道
Damn it, slow down! I can't stay on the course!

741
00:51:15,634 --> 00:51:18,220
你會撞上山壁，小心…
You're gonna hit the wall! Watch out! Watch out!

742
00:51:21,932 --> 00:51:24,643
-怎麼回事？
-我飛到最快
-What happened?
-I flew as fast as I could.

743
00:51:25,227 --> 00:51:26,812
像是火燒屁股一樣
Kind of like my ass depended on it.

744
00:51:26,895 --> 00:51:30,107
你危及到隊友，僚機也掛了
And you put your team in danger, and your wingman's dead.

745
00:51:31,316 --> 00:51:32,859
他們跟不上我
They couldn't keep up.

746
00:51:38,991 --> 00:51:41,618
公雞，我們落後20秒
Rooster, we're 20 seconds behind and dropping.

747
00:51:41,702 --> 00:51:44,288
沒問題，速度可以
We're fine. Speed is good.

748
00:51:44,371 --> 00:51:45,914
加速到500節
Increase to 500 knots.

749
00:51:45,998 --> 00:51:49,042
-不，耶魯，別加速
-我們落後了
-Negative, Yale. Hold your speed.
-Rooster, we're late!

750
00:51:49,126 --> 00:51:51,920
我們還活著，直飛時再趕進度
We're alive. We'll make up time in the straightaway.

751
00:51:52,004 --> 00:51:53,588
我們會來不及
We are not gonna make it.

752
00:51:53,672 --> 00:51:56,675
相信我，保持速度，趕得到的
Just trust me. Maintain your speed. We can make it.

753
00:51:56,758 --> 00:51:57,884
你為什麼會死？
Why are you dead?

754
00:51:59,219 --> 00:52:03,181
你是隊長，隊友為什麼會死？
You're team leader up there.
Why are you, why is your team dead?

755
00:52:03,265 --> 00:52:05,934
長官，只有他抵達目標
Sir, he's the only one who made it to the target.

756
00:52:06,018 --> 00:52:07,227
遲了一分鐘
A minute late.

757
00:52:08,020 --> 00:52:10,606
他給敵機時間擊落他
He gave enemy aircraft time to shoot him down.

758
00:52:10,689 --> 00:52:12,524
-他死了
-你不能確定
-He is dead.
-You don't know that.

759
00:52:12,608 --> 00:52:16,111
你飛得太慢，浪費了時間
You're not flying fast enough.
You don't have a second to waste.

760
00:52:16,194 --> 00:52:17,446
我們成功抵達目標
We made it to the target.

761
00:52:17,529 --> 00:52:21,241
更優越的敵機在返航時攔截你
And superior enemy aircraft intercepted you on your way out.

762
00:52:21,325 --> 00:52:24,328
-那就展開空戰
-對上第五代戰機
-Then it's a dogfight.
-Against fifth-generation fighters.

763
00:52:24,411 --> 00:52:26,997
-還是有機會
-F-18戰機贏不了
-Yeah. We'd still have a chance.
-In an F-18.

764
00:52:27,080 --> 00:52:29,583
關鍵不是在戰機…而是飛行員
It's not the plane, sir, it's the pilot.

765
00:52:29,666 --> 00:52:30,792
一點也沒錯
Exactly!

766
00:52:37,924 --> 00:52:40,594
執行這任務有別的方法
There's more than one way to fly this mission.

767
00:52:40,677 --> 00:52:42,638
你真的沒搞懂
You really don't get it.

768
00:52:43,639 --> 00:52:46,308
執行這任務就得像獨行俠那樣飛
On this mission, a man flies like Maverick here,

769
00:52:46,391 --> 00:52:48,226
否則就不可能回來
or a man does not come back.

770
00:52:49,227 --> 00:52:51,313
無意冒犯
No offense intended.

771
00:52:51,396 --> 00:52:53,690
但你卻老是惹毛我們
Yet somehow you always manage.

772
00:52:55,233 --> 00:52:58,028
我不是批評你，只是你太保守了
Look, I don't mean to criticize.
You're conservative, that's all.

773
00:52:58,111 --> 00:52:58,946
中尉
Lieutenant.

774
00:52:59,029 --> 00:53:03,617
我們將進行…沒有飛行員嘗試過的空戰
We're going into combat, son,
on a level no living pilot's ever seen.

775
00:53:05,160 --> 00:53:06,286
就連他也沒有過
Not even him.

776
00:53:08,288 --> 00:53:10,123
沒時間糾結過去的事
That's no time to be thinking about the past.

777
00:53:14,211 --> 00:53:16,254
-那是啥意思？
-公雞
-What's that supposed to mean?
-Rooster.

778
00:53:16,338 --> 00:53:18,924
大家都知道他老爸和獨行俠一起飛過
I can't be the only one that knows
that Maverick flew with his old man.

779
00:53:19,007 --> 00:53:20,467
-夠了
-或者是獨行俠
-That's enough.
-Or that Maverick was flying

780
00:53:20,550 --> 00:53:22,260
-害死他老爸…
-中尉，夠了！
-when his old man--
-Lieutenant, that's enough!

781
00:53:24,221 --> 00:53:26,098
-夠了
-你這王八蛋
-That's enough.
-You son of a bitch!

782
00:53:26,181 --> 00:53:27,140
嘿，別這樣！
Hey, come on!

783
00:53:27,224 --> 00:53:29,726
我沒事，嘿嘿嘿
I'm cool, I'm cool. Hey, hey, hey.

784
00:53:29,810 --> 00:53:30,644
夠了
That's enough.

785
00:53:30,727 --> 00:53:32,813
-他不夠資格出任務
-夠了
-He's not cut out for this mission.
-That's enough!

786
00:53:32,896 --> 00:53:34,147
你明明知道
You know it.

787
00:53:37,192 --> 00:53:38,193
你知道我是對的
You know I'm right.

788
00:53:44,658 --> 00:53:45,784
全員解散
You're all dismissed.

789
00:54:01,174 --> 00:54:03,844
（冰人：“我得見你”）

790
00:54:08,473 --> 00:54:11,935
（不太方便）

791
00:54:12,019 --> 00:54:14,730
（冰人：“我沒在問你”）

792
00:54:50,098 --> 00:54:51,475
獨行俠
Maverick.

793
00:54:53,810 --> 00:54:55,103
又復發了？
It's come back?

794
00:54:55,771 --> 00:54:57,230
沒人知道
No one knows.

795
00:54:59,399 --> 00:55:01,109
醫生也無能為力
There's nothing else they can do.

796
00:55:01,985 --> 00:55:04,988
他連說話都很痛苦
Even speaking is painful now.

797
00:55:10,994 --> 00:55:12,704
莎拉，真的很抱歉
Sarah, I'm so sorry.

798
00:55:32,391 --> 00:55:33,392
上將
Admiral.

799
00:55:44,945 --> 00:55:46,154
我的僚機駕駛員還好嗎？
How's my wingman?

800
00:55:52,202 --> 00:55:55,956
（我想談談工作）

801
00:55:57,791 --> 00:56:00,085
沒事…別替我擔心
Please, don't worry about me.

802
00:56:01,044 --> 00:56:02,796
我能做什麼？
What can I do for you?

803
00:56:11,263 --> 00:56:12,347
好吧
All right.

804
00:56:15,183 --> 00:56:18,312
公雞還在為我做的事生氣
Well, Rooster's still angry with me about what I did.

805
00:56:19,813 --> 00:56:22,566
我以為他有一天能理解
I thought eventually he would understand why.

806
00:56:24,818 --> 00:56:26,486
也希望他能原諒我
I hoped he'd forgive me.

807
00:56:28,780 --> 00:56:32,409
（還有時間）

808
00:56:34,911 --> 00:56:36,830
任務只剩下不到三禮拜
The mission is less than three weeks away.

809
00:56:37,414 --> 00:56:38,999
那孩子沒準備好
The kid's not ready.

810
00:56:41,126 --> 00:56:44,963
（那就教好他）

811
00:56:47,341 --> 00:56:49,301
他不要我教
He doesn't want what I have to give.

812
00:56:50,510 --> 00:56:51,762
冰人，拜託
Ice, please,

813
00:56:51,845 --> 00:56:54,181
別要求我派別人去赴死
don't ask me to send someone else to die.

814
00:56:54,264 --> 00:56:55,390
別這麼做
Please don't…

815
00:56:56,391 --> 00:56:57,976
別要我派他去
Don't ask me to send him.

816
00:56:58,060 --> 00:56:59,645
派我去
Send me.

817
00:57:13,492 --> 00:57:17,746
（該放手了）

818
00:57:31,426 --> 00:57:33,095
我不知道該如何放手
I don't know how.

819
00:57:46,316 --> 00:57:48,068
我不是教官，冰人
I'm not a teacher, Ice.

820
00:57:50,487 --> 00:57:52,322
我是戰機駕駛員
I'm a fighter pilot.

821
00:57:54,908 --> 00:57:56,326
海軍飛行員
A naval aviator.

822
00:57:58,829 --> 00:58:00,914
那不僅僅是工作職稱
It's not what I am.

823
00:58:02,165 --> 00:58:03,750
而是我與生俱來的能力
It's who I am.

824
00:58:05,502 --> 00:58:07,254
我該怎麼教這種事?
How do I teach that?

825
00:58:09,131 --> 00:58:11,758
就算可以，也不是公雞要的
Even if I could teach it, it's not what Rooster wants.

826
00:58:12,718 --> 00:58:14,886
更不是海軍要的
It's not what the navy wants.

827
00:58:14,970 --> 00:58:17,306
所以上次我才會被開除
That's why they canned me the last time.

828
00:58:20,142 --> 00:58:23,103
我之所以還能在海軍是因為你
The only reason I'm here is you.

829
00:58:30,444 --> 00:58:32,279
如果我派他出這項任務
If I send him on this mission,

830
00:58:33,697 --> 00:58:35,574
他可能就此一去不回
he might never come home.

831
00:58:39,328 --> 00:58:40,954
但若不派他去
And if I don't send him,

832
00:58:41,663 --> 00:58:43,498
他絕對不會原諒我
he'll never forgive me.

833
00:58:46,209 --> 00:58:48,670
不管怎樣，我都將永遠失去他
Either way, I could lose him forever.

834
00:58:59,139 --> 00:59:00,140
我知道
I know.

835
00:59:00,974 --> 00:59:02,309
我知道
I know.

836
00:59:13,487 --> 00:59:17,115
海軍…需要獨行俠
The navy needs Maverick.

837
00:59:19,159 --> 00:59:22,704
那孩子需要獨行俠
The kid needs Maverick.

838
00:59:23,789 --> 00:59:26,041
這是為什麼我極力為你爭取
That's why I fought for you.

839
00:59:28,043 --> 00:59:30,379
這也是為什麼你仍然在這裡
That's why you're still here.

840
00:59:38,428 --> 00:59:40,180
謝謝你，冰人
Thank you, Ice,

841
00:59:40,847 --> 00:59:42,265
為我所做的一切
for everything.

842
00:59:47,187 --> 00:59:48,647
最後一件事
One last thing.

843
00:59:49,273 --> 00:59:51,024
誰是比較厲害的飛行員？
Who's the better pilot?

844
