我猜我發現…
I guess I realized

892
01:04:38,478 --> 01:04:40,564
我也必須信任她
I also had to trust her.

893
01:04:42,149 --> 01:04:44,651
偶爾讓她自己犯些錯
Let her make some of her own mistakes sometimes.

894
01:04:47,154 --> 01:04:48,822
這決定不容易
Not an easy choice.

895
01:04:53,160 --> 01:04:55,162
你和公雞是怎麼回事？
Is that what happened with Rooster?

896
01:04:58,832 --> 01:05:01,585
我拿掉他的海軍官校申請書
I pulled his papers from the Naval Academy.

897
01:05:04,630 --> 01:05:06,340
浪費了他幾年時間
Took years off his career.

898
01:05:12,638 --> 01:05:13,639
為什麼？
Why?

899
01:05:16,558 --> 01:05:20,062
呆頭鵝死後，他母親不希望他當飛官
His mother never wanted him to fly,
not after what happened to Goose.

900
01:05:22,856 --> 01:05:26,276
她死前要我答應她，所以…
She made me promise before she died, so…

901
01:05:26,360 --> 01:05:28,278
公雞知道嗎？
Does Rooster know that?

902
01:05:31,823 --> 01:05:34,868
他永遠會為這件事恨我
He will always resent me for what I did.

903
01:05:36,870 --> 01:05:38,872
沒必要讓他也恨她
Why should he resent her too?

904
01:05:43,794 --> 01:05:45,504
這決定不容易
Not an easy choice.

905
01:05:48,465 --> 01:05:50,968
我試著當他失去的父親
I was trying to be the father he lost.

906
01:05:54,054 --> 01:05:55,055
只是…
I just--

907
01:05:57,933 --> 01:06:00,102
我希望能做得更好
I wish I would've done it better.

908
01:06:02,354 --> 01:06:05,190
但是…事實是
But the truth is…

909
01:06:07,734 --> 01:06:09,569
我認為他還沒準備好
I didn't think he was ready.

910
01:06:13,156 --> 01:06:14,866
現在呢？
Is he ready now?

911
01:06:18,328 --> 01:06:19,746
媽，我回家了！
Mom, I'm home!

912
01:06:21,498 --> 01:06:23,917
我以為妳要在凱倫家過夜
I thought you were staying at Karen's tonight.

913
01:06:24,001 --> 01:06:26,753
凱倫生病，我有功課要做
Karen's sick. And I've got homework to do.

914
01:06:26,837 --> 01:06:29,256
-我該走了
-你該走了
-I should go.
-You should go.

915
01:06:29,840 --> 01:06:32,634
-吃過飯嗎？
-還沒，要出去吃嗎？
-Have you had dinner yet?
-Not yet. You want to go out?

916
01:06:32,718 --> 01:06:35,679
沒關係，我做給妳吃
No, it's okay. I'll make you something.

917
01:06:35,762 --> 01:06:36,847
馬上就下去
I'll be down in a sec!

918
01:06:37,723 --> 01:06:39,683
-等等，別走那兒
-什麼？
-Wait! Not that way.
-What?

919
01:06:41,351 --> 01:06:43,562
我得當個好榜樣
Look, I have an example to set.

920
01:06:43,645 --> 01:06:46,106
不能第一次約會就帶男人回家
I can't be bringing guys home on a first date.

921
01:06:46,189 --> 01:06:47,524
這不是第一次約會
This is not our first date.

922
01:06:48,692 --> 01:06:50,235
你懂我的意思
You know what I mean.

923
01:06:52,988 --> 01:06:53,989
好吧
Okay.

924
01:06:55,157 --> 01:06:56,199
好吧
Fine.

925
01:06:57,242 --> 01:06:59,536
這是我最後一次跳出妳家窗戶
But this is the last time I go out your window.

926
01:06:59,620 --> 01:07:01,079
再說吧
We'll see.

927
01:07:01,163 --> 01:07:02,581
我是說真的
No. No, I mean it.

928
01:07:03,332 --> 01:07:05,250
我永遠不會再離開妳
I'm never gonna leave you again.

929
01:07:07,252 --> 01:07:08,879
閉嘴啦
Oh, shut up.

930
01:07:08,962 --> 01:07:10,839
快走吧
Go on, get out of here.

931
01:07:24,394 --> 01:07:26,355
別再傷她的心
Just don't break her heart again.

932
01:07:38,325 --> 01:07:39,326
早安
Good morning.

933
01:07:39,409 --> 01:07:41,536
你們的目標鈾濃縮工廠
The uranium enrichment plant that is your target

934
01:07:41,620 --> 01:07:44,081
將會提早開始運作
will be operational earlier than expected.

935
01:07:44,164 --> 01:07:47,292
天然鈾在十天內會送到工廠
Raw uranium will be delivered to the plant in ten days' time.

936
01:07:48,001 --> 01:07:51,088
所以你們的任務也提前一星期
As a result, your mission has been moved up one week

937
01:07:51,171 --> 01:07:54,800
以免那座峽谷受到輻射汙染
in order to avoid contaminating
the target valley with radiation.

938
01:07:54,883 --> 01:07:57,719
長官，這裡沒人成功完成低空航道飛行
Sir, no one here has successfully flown a low-level course.

939
01:07:57,803 --> 01:07:59,721
但你們仍被命令繼續下去
Nevertheless, you've been ordered to move on.

940
01:08:00,931 --> 01:08:01,932
上校
Captain.

941
01:08:04,977 --> 01:08:07,354
只剩一星期進行第二階段演練
We have one week left to focus on phase two.

942
01:08:07,437 --> 01:08:09,314
那是這項任務最困難的階段
It's the most difficult stage of the mission.

943
01:08:09,398 --> 01:08:11,191
那是俯衝突襲行動
It's a pop-up strike with a steep dive,

944
01:08:11,275 --> 01:08:14,194
需要連續出現兩個奇蹟
requiring nothing less than two consecutive miracles.

945
01:08:15,362 --> 01:08:18,532
兩組戰機要以並列隊形飛行
Two pairs of F-18s will fly in a welded wing formation.

946
01:08:18,615 --> 01:08:19,865
團隊合作
Teamwork.

947
01:08:19,950 --> 01:08:22,452
飛行的精準度是這項任務成功…
Precise coordination of these aircraft is essential

948
01:08:22,535 --> 01:08:25,247
和你們存活的關鍵
to both the mission's success and your survival.

949
01:08:25,329 --> 01:08:28,041
工廠坐落在兩座山脈之間
As you know, the plant rests between two mountains.

950
01:08:28,166 --> 01:08:32,212
逼近時要倒栽蔥直接俯衝
On final approach, you'll invert directly into a steep dive.

951
01:08:33,213 --> 01:08:35,882
這樣才能保持低空飛行
This allows you to maintain the lowest possible altitude

952
01:08:37,092 --> 01:08:38,885
也是唯一的攻擊角度
and the only possible attack angle.

953
01:08:42,638 --> 01:08:46,476
目標的彈著點不到三米寬
Your target is an impact point less than three meters wide.

954
01:08:47,727 --> 01:08:50,646
兩人座戰機將以雷射標示靶點
The two-seat aircraft will paint
the target with a laser bull's-eye.

955
01:08:52,106 --> 01:08:53,984
第一組將發射雷射引導飛彈
The first pair will breach the reactor

956
01:08:54,066 --> 01:08:57,738
進入通風口炸毀反應爐
by dropping a laser-guided bomb
on an exposed ventilation hatch.

957
01:08:57,820 --> 01:09:00,032
這會為第二組製造空檔
This will create an opening for the second pair.

958
01:09:00,865 --> 01:09:02,325
那是第一個奇蹟
That's miracle number one.

959
01:09:04,620 --> 01:09:06,079
第二組…
The second team

960
01:09:06,163 --> 01:09:07,497
將做出必殺一擊
will deliver the kill shot

961
01:09:08,832 --> 01:09:10,626
徹底摧毀目標
and destroy the target.

962
01:09:11,877 --> 01:09:13,211
那是第二個奇蹟
That's miracle number two.

963
01:09:14,588 --> 01:09:16,840
兩組都沒有命中目標…
If either team misses the target…

964
01:09:19,133 --> 01:09:20,010
未命中
That's a miss.

965
01:09:20,093 --> 01:09:22,095
-任務就失敗
-可惡
-Damn it!

966
01:09:22,803 --> 01:09:26,600
飛離時必須垂直爬升，以免撞到山壁
Egress is a steep high-G climb out
to avoid hitting this mountain.

967
01:09:29,477 --> 01:09:32,773
高速垂直爬升至少會承受8個G力
A steep climb at that speed, you're pulling at least eight G's.

968
01:09:32,856 --> 01:09:34,358
至少9個G力
Nine, minimum.

969
01:09:34,441 --> 01:09:37,235
F-18機身的極限應力是7.5
The stress limit of the F-18's airframe is 7.5.

970
01:09:37,319 --> 01:09:38,695
那是可接受的極限
That's the accepted limit.

971
01:09:38,779 --> 01:09:40,989
想活著回來就得超越極限
To survive this mission, you'll pull beyond that,

972
01:09:41,073 --> 01:09:43,742
就算必須折彎機身
even if it means bending your airframe.

973
01:09:45,077 --> 01:09:48,454
重力大到你們會重達900公斤
You'll be pulling so hard, you'll weigh close to 2,000 pounds,

974
01:09:48,538 --> 01:09:51,416
頭蓋骨會擠壓脊椎
your skull crushing your spine,

975
01:09:51,541 --> 01:09:54,586
像被一頭大象坐在胸口擠壓肺部
your lungs imploding like an elephant's sitting on your chest,

976
01:09:54,670 --> 01:09:58,090
拼了命也要避免昏厥過去
fighting with everything you have
just to keep from blacking out.

977
01:10:00,175 --> 01:10:02,678
這是你們最脆弱的時刻
And this is where you'll be at your most vulnerable.

978
01:10:03,637 --> 01:10:06,515
這就是棺材角
This is Coffin Corner.

979
01:10:06,598 --> 01:10:09,351
就算你們沒撞上山壁
Assuming you avoid crashing into this mountain,

980
01:10:09,434 --> 01:10:13,021
也會爬升到敵軍雷達範圍內
同時完全失速
you'll climb straight up into enemy radar
while losing all of your airspeed.

981
01:10:13,605 --> 01:10:16,233
這時候將遇到敵軍飛彈攻擊
Within seconds, you'll be fired upon by enemy SAMs.

982
01:10:17,734 --> 01:10:19,945
你們都承受過G力，但這次…
You've all faced sustained G's before, but this--

983
01:10:20,696 --> 01:10:24,366
將把你們和戰機逼到臨界點
this is gonna take you and your aircraft to the breaking point.

984
01:10:24,449 --> 01:10:27,202
長官，有可能成功嗎？
Sir, is this even achievable?

985
01:10:27,286 --> 01:10:28,954
這個問題的答案…
The answer to that question

986
01:10:29,538 --> 01:10:31,540
取決於駕駛艙內的飛行員
will come down to the pilot in the box.

987
01:10:41,466 --> 01:10:43,719
-回報狀況，巴布
-我們落後12秒
-Talk to me, Bob.
-We are 12 seconds late on target.

988
01:10:43,802 --> 01:10:46,513
-必須加速…
-收到，試著跟上來
-We got to move! We got to move!
-Copy. Try to stay with me.

989
01:10:50,517 --> 01:10:51,727
等等，那是誰？
Wait, who's that?

990
01:10:53,020 --> 01:10:54,396
藍組，你們被偵測到
Blue Team, you've been spotted.

991
01:10:54,479 --> 01:10:57,107
-靠，是獨行俠
-他跑來幹嘛？
-Shit, it's Maverick.
-What the hell is he doing here?

992
01:10:57,190 --> 01:11:00,319
我是來攔截的敵機，你們要怎麼辦？
I'm a bandit on course to intercept.
Blue Team, what are you gonna do?

993
01:11:00,402 --> 01:11:03,614
左翼20哩，10點鐘方向，700節
He's 20 miles left. Ten o'clock. 700 knots closure.

994
01:11:03,697 --> 01:11:05,532
妳決定，妳要怎麼做？
Your call. What do you want to do?

995
01:11:05,616 --> 01:11:08,327
繼續下去，就快接近目標了
Continue. We're close. Stay on target.

996
01:11:08,410 --> 01:11:11,622
-他繞到北方
-準備爬升
-He's swinging around to the north!
-Stand by for pop-up.

997
01:11:11,705 --> 01:11:13,790
-準備雷射引導
-收到
-Be ready on that laser, Bob.
-Copy. I'm on it.

998
01:11:16,043 --> 01:11:17,753
藍組，敵機逼近中
Blue Team, bandit is still closing.

999
01:11:17,836 --> 01:11:19,004
爬升
Popping now.

1000
01:11:25,177 --> 01:11:27,304
回報狀況，巴布，獨行俠呢？
Talk to me, Bob. Where's Maverick?

1001
01:11:27,387 --> 01:11:29,431
他在五哩外，快速逼近
He's five miles out. He's coming fast.

1002
01:11:35,312 --> 01:11:37,814
-看到目標
-雷射呢？
-Target's in sight.
-Where's my laser, Bob?

1003
01:11:38,649 --> 01:11:42,027
無法瞄準…抱歉，無法鎖定目標
Deadeye! Deadeye! It's no good. Sorry, I can't get a lock.

1004
01:11:42,110 --> 01:11:43,946
來不及了，我要盲投炸彈
We're out of time. I'm dropping blind.

1005
01:11:47,199 --> 01:11:48,617
該死，沒命中
Damn it, missed!

1006
01:12:00,212 --> 01:12:02,381
-鎖定你了
-獨行俠的飛彈鎖定我們
-That's tone.
-Maverick's got missile lock on us.

1007
01:12:02,464 --> 01:12:03,507
靠，我們掛了
Shit! We're dead.

1008
01:12:04,341 --> 01:12:07,094
藍組，任務失敗，停止爬升
Blue Team, that's a fail. Level out, Coyote.

1009
01:12:09,763 --> 01:12:11,682
郊狼？收到嗎？
Coyote? Do you copy?

1010
01:12:14,518 --> 01:12:15,978
郊狼，回答
Coyote, come in.

1011
01:12:16,603 --> 01:12:18,522
郊狼，拉直
Coyote, level wings.

1012
01:12:18,605 --> 01:12:20,190
天啊，他進入G力昏迷
Oh, God. He's in G-LOC.

1013
01:12:20,941 --> 01:12:23,485
郊狼？郊狼？
Coyote? Coyote?

1014
01:12:23,568 --> 01:12:25,779
-他會墜機
-我去追他
-He's gonna burn in!
-I'm going after him.

1015
01:12:29,491 --> 01:12:31,785
快啊，快點鎖定…
Come on. Give me tone, give me tone, give me tone.

1016
01:12:32,327 --> 01:12:34,746
快醒醒，郊狼，快啊…
Snap out of it, Coyote. Come on! Come on!

1017
01:12:37,791 --> 01:12:40,544
加油，郊狼，快啊，快啊！
Come on, Coyote, come on. Come on!

1018
01:12:40,627 --> 01:12:42,796
-該死，郊狼…
-爬升
-Damn it! Coyote!
-Pull up!

1019
01:12:42,879 --> 01:12:45,507
-郊狼…
-爬升…
-Coyote! Coyote!
-Pull up! Pull up!

1020
01:12:50,721 --> 01:12:52,514
郊狼，沒事吧？
Coyote, you okay?

1021
01:12:53,557 --> 01:12:55,309
我沒事
I'm okay. I'm good.

1022
01:12:56,310 --> 01:12:59,146
那就好，今天演練夠了
Good. Good. That's enough for today.

1023
01:13:01,356 --> 01:13:02,566
好險喔
That was close.

1024
01:13:03,150 --> 01:13:04,067
太危險了
Too close.

1025
01:13:04,943 --> 01:13:07,112
鳥擊！
Bird strike! Bird strike!

1026
01:13:07,195 --> 01:13:08,322
鳥擊！
Bird strike!

1027
01:13:11,658 --> 01:13:14,328
-鳳凰，左引擎起火
-爬升
-Phoenix, left engine's on fire!
-Climbing.

1028
01:13:16,330 --> 01:13:18,832
減速，關閉左引擎燃油
Throttling back. Shutting off fuel to left engine.

1029
01:13:18,915 --> 01:13:20,542
滅火
Extinguishing fire.

1030
01:13:22,919 --> 01:13:23,920
右引擎故障
Right engine is out!

1031
01:13:24,004 --> 01:13:25,672
渦輪還在旋轉，試圖重新啟動
It's still spinning. Trying to restart it.

1032
01:13:28,175 --> 01:13:30,802
-鳳凰，起火了，別啟動
-加速
-Phoenix, it's on fire. Don't start it.
-Throttling up.

1033
01:13:32,387 --> 01:13:33,639
我的天啊
Oh, my God.

1034
01:13:37,017 --> 01:13:39,436
-起火了…
-該死
-We're on fire! We're on fire!
-Damn it!

1035
01:13:39,519 --> 01:13:42,272
-右引擎起火
-熄滅右引擎
-Engine fire. Right.
-Extinguishing right engine.

1036
01:13:45,567 --> 01:13:47,486
鳳凰、巴布，快彈跳，快彈跳！
Phoenix, Bob, punch out, punch out!

1037
01:13:47,569 --> 01:13:49,780
警示燈都亮著，液壓系統失靈
Warning lights everywhere! Hydraulic failure!

1038
01:13:49,863 --> 01:13:51,573
-操縱失效
-我無法控制了
-Flight controls.
-I can't control it.

1039
01:13:51,657 --> 01:13:54,409
我們要墜機了，鳳凰
我們要墜入山谷了…
We're going down, Phoenix! We're going in! We're going in!

1040
01:13:54,493 --> 01:13:57,120
沒救了，快彈跳…
You can't save it. Eject, eject!

1041
01:13:57,204 --> 01:13:58,372
彈跳…彈跳…
Eject, eject, eject!

1042
01:13:58,455 --> 01:14:01,291
高度，高度
Altitude. Altitude.

1043
01:14:22,813 --> 01:14:25,816
鳳凰和巴布要在醫院過夜接受觀察
They'll keep Phoenix and Bob
in the hospital overnight for observation.

1044
01:14:25,899 --> 01:14:27,401
他們不會有事
They're gonna be okay.

1045
01:14:31,488 --> 01:14:32,823
那就好
That's good.

1046
01:14:36,076 --> 01:14:37,911
我從未失去過僚機
I've never lost a wingman.

1047
01:14:38,662 --> 01:14:39,871
你很幸運
You're lucky.

1048
01:14:40,455 --> 01:14:42,291
飛得夠久，就會發生
Fly long enough, it'll happen.

1049
01:14:45,085 --> 01:14:46,753
會有其他人
There will be others.

1050
01:14:49,506 --> 01:14:51,508
你說得倒容易，沒有老婆
Easy for you to say. No wife.

1051
01:14:53,468 --> 01:14:54,678
沒有小孩
No kids.

1052
01:14:55,512 --> 01:14:58,015
掛了也不會有人悼念你
Nobody to mourn you when you burn in.

1053
01:15:01,268 --> 01:15:02,603
回家吧
Go home.

1054
01:15:03,729 --> 01:15:05,188
好好睡個覺吧
Just get some sleep.

1055
01:15:07,733 --> 01:15:09,943
你為什麼拿掉我官校的申請書？
Why'd you pull my papers at the Academy?

1056
01:15:10,027 --> 01:15:11,653
為什麼擋我的路？
Why did you stand in my way?

1057
01:15:14,239 --> 01:15:15,574
你當時還沒準備好
You weren't ready.

1058
01:15:15,657 --> 01:15:16,950
準備好什麼？
Ready for what?

1059
01:15:18,619 --> 01:15:20,412
-像你那樣亂飛？
-不
-Ready to fly like you?
-No.

1060
01:15:20,495 --> 01:15:22,122
準備忘記書本裡的規則
Ready to forget the book.

1061
01:15:22,205 --> 01:15:24,916
相信直覺，別猶豫，放手去做
Trust your instincts. Don't think, just do.

1062
01:15:25,000 --> 01:15:27,669
只要猶豫就會死，相信我
You think up there, you're dead. Believe me.

1063
01:15:28,962 --> 01:15:30,631
我爸相信你
My dad believed in you.

1064
01:15:33,342 --> 01:15:35,802
但我不會犯同樣的錯
I'm not gonna make the same mistake.

1065
01:15:41,475 --> 01:15:42,976
獨行俠
Maverick.

1066
01:15:53,528 --> 01:15:56,406
預備、瞄準、射擊
Ready, aim, fire.

1067
01:16:01,161 --> 01:16:02,329
預備
Ready,

1068
01:16:02,829 --> 01:16:03,872
瞄準
aim,

1069
01:16:04,414 --> 01:16:05,749
射擊
fire.

1070
01:16:15,801 --> 01:16:17,010
Ready,

1071
01:16:18,053 --> 01:16:19,429
aim,

1072
01:16:19,513 --> 01:16:20,806
fire.

1073
01:16:54,589 --> 01:16:56,758
我無法體會你現在的感受
I can only imagine what you must be feeling right now.

1074
01:16:57,843 --> 01:17:00,095
想休息幾天就休息幾天
Take some time. Whatever you need.

1075
01:17:01,555 --> 01:17:03,724
謝謝你，長官，但是任務…
I appreciate that, sir, but there is no time. The mission--

1076
01:17:03,807 --> 01:17:05,892
我會接手訓練他們
I'll be taking over the training from here.

1077
01:17:06,893 --> 01:17:07,894
長官？
Sir?

1078
01:17:09,313 --> 01:17:11,106
我們都知道你不想要這工作
We both know you didn't want this job, Captain.

1079
01:17:11,189 --> 01:17:13,525
-他們還沒準備好
-那是你的工作
-Sir, they're not ready.
-It was your job to get them ready.

1080
01:17:13,609 --> 01:17:17,070
他們必須相信能達成這項任務
Sir, they have to believe that this mission can be flown.

1081
01:17:17,154 --> 01:17:19,906
你卻只讓他們認為任務會失敗
And all you've managed to do is teach them that it can't.

1082
01:17:20,741 --> 01:17:23,076
-長官…
-你被禁飛了
-Sir--
-You're grounded, Captain.

1083
01:17:23,160 --> 01:17:24,661
永遠禁飛
Permanently.

1084
01:17:28,540 --> 01:17:29,833
-長官…
-就這樣
-Sir--
-That is all.

1085
01:17:48,352 --> 01:17:49,353
我聽說了
I heard.

1086
01:17:51,647 --> 01:17:52,814
很遺憾
I'm sorry.

1087
01:17:53,690 --> 01:17:55,359
你有什麼打算？
What are you gonna do?

1088
01:17:56,526 --> 01:17:57,819
冰人走了
Ice is gone.

1089
01:18:00,364 --> 01:18:02,074
我還能有什麼選擇？
What choice do I have?

1090
01:18:03,283 --> 01:18:05,869
你會找到繼續飛的方法
You'll have to find a way back on your own.

1091
01:18:05,953 --> 01:18:07,204
不，潘妮
No, Penny.

1092
01:18:08,997 --> 01:18:10,332
我已出局
I'm out.

1093
01:18:12,084 --> 01:18:13,335
軍旅生涯結束了
This is over.

1094
01:18:13,877 --> 01:18:14,878
彼得…
Pete.

1095
01:18:14,962 --> 01:18:17,422
就算失去你的僚機
If you lost your wingman up there,

1096
01:18:18,173 --> 01:18:19,883
還是會繼續奮戰
you'd keep fighting.

1097
01:18:19,967 --> 01:18:21,259
不會放棄
You wouldn't just give up.

1098
01:18:22,052 --> 01:18:24,012
他們是你的飛行員
Those are your pilots.

1099
01:18:25,305 --> 01:18:27,474
要是他們出事…
If anything happens to them,

1100
01:18:28,308 --> 01:18:30,352
你會永遠無法原諒自己
you'll never forgive yourself.

1101
01:18:34,398 --> 01:18:36,275
我不知道該怎麼做
I don't know what to do.

1102
01:18:40,320 --> 01:18:41,863
你會找到方法的
But you'll find a way.

1103
01:18:44,283 --> 01:18:45,492
你一定會的
I know you will.

1104
01:18:47,661 --> 01:18:50,038
米契爾上校不再是你們的教官
Captain Mitchell is no longer your instructor.

1105
01:18:50,122 --> 01:18:52,541
從今天起有新的任務參數
And as of today, there are new mission parameters.

1106
01:18:53,292 --> 01:18:55,168
抵達目標時間是四分鐘
Time to target is now four minutes.

1107
01:18:55,919 --> 01:18:58,463
你們將減速平飛進入峽谷
You'll be entering the valley level at reduced speed.

1108
01:18:58,547 --> 01:19:01,508
不准超過420節
Not to exceed 420 knots.

1109
01:19:01,591 --> 01:19:04,386
敵機不就有時間進行攔截？
Sir, won't we be giving their planes time to intercept?

1110
01:19:04,469 --> 01:19:06,972
對上敵機至少還有機會存活
Well, Lieutenant, you have
a fighting chance against enemy aircraft.

1111
01:19:07,055 --> 01:19:10,142
撞上山壁存活的機率是多少？
What are the odds of surviving
a head-on collision with a mountain?

1112
01:19:10,225 --> 01:19:12,811
你們要沿著北邊山壁
You'll be attacking the target from a higher altitude,

1113
01:19:12,894 --> 01:19:14,104
從更高的高度攻擊目標
level with the north wall.

1114
01:19:14,187 --> 01:19:16,607
這會更難以雷射標示目標
Gonna be a little harder to keep your lase on target,

1115
01:19:16,690 --> 01:19:18,609
但能避免高G力爬升
but you will avoid the high-G climb out.

1116
01:19:18,692 --> 01:19:20,902
敵方飛彈會擊落我們
We'll be sitting ducks for enemy missiles.

1117
01:19:26,325 --> 01:19:27,576
那是誰？
Who the hell is that?

1118
01:19:29,369 --> 01:19:32,205
獨行俠呼叫控制中心，進入A點
Maverick to Range Control. Entering Point Alpha.

1119
01:19:32,289 --> 01:19:33,957
請確認安全
Confirm green range.

1120
01:19:34,583 --> 01:19:36,918
這是控制中心…
Maverick, Range Control,

1121
01:19:37,002 --> 01:19:38,629
確認安全
green range is confirmed.

1122
01:19:38,712 --> 01:19:42,090
我沒看到你的演練行程
I don't see an event scheduled for you, sir.

1123
01:19:42,174 --> 01:19:43,383
我還是要去
Well, I'm going anyway.

1124
01:19:44,051 --> 01:19:45,302
水啦
Nice.

1125
01:19:46,053 --> 01:19:49,097
設定目標時間：2分15秒
Setting time to target: Two minutes 15 seconds.

1126
01:19:49,181 --> 01:19:50,932
2分15秒？不可能
2:15? That's impossible.

1127
01:19:51,016 --> 01:19:53,560
獨行俠飛往最終攻擊點
Final attack point. Maverick's inbound.

1128
01:21:31,241 --> 01:21:34,453
倒數三、二、一，爬升
Popping in three, two, one.

1129
01:22:00,938 --> 01:22:02,314
投擲炸彈
Bombs away.

1130
01:22:19,790 --> 01:22:21,708
正中目標！哇靠！
Bull's-eye! Holy shit!

1131
01:22:23,001 --> 01:22:24,586
厲害
Yes.

1132
01:22:27,464 --> 01:22:28,590
帥
Damn.

1133
01:22:41,353 --> 01:22:43,563
你讓我左右為難，上校
You have put me in a difficult position, Captain.

1134
01:22:44,481 --> 01:22:48,235
你一方面示範了任務的可行性
On the one hand, you have demonstrated
that this mission can be flown.

1135
01:22:48,318 --> 01:22:50,404
也許是唯一存活的方法
Perhaps the only way it can be survived.

1136
01:22:51,822 --> 01:22:53,532
另一方面…
On the other hand,

1137
01:22:53,615 --> 01:22:56,535
你偷開走一架數百萬美金的戰機
you did it by stealing a multimillion-dollar military aircraft

1138
01:22:56,618 --> 01:22:59,496
把它操到可能永遠無法再飛行
and flying it in such a manner
that it may never be airworthy again.

1139
01:23:00,914 --> 01:23:03,208
冰人不能再保護你了
Iceman is no longer here to protect you.

1140
01:23:04,042 --> 01:23:06,670
我大可以把你送去軍事法庭
I have everything I need to have you court-martialed

1141
01:23:06,753 --> 01:23:08,505
讓你不榮譽退伍
and dishonorably discharged.

1142
01:23:09,298 --> 01:23:10,674
我該怎麼做？
So what do I do?

1143
01:23:11,675 --> 01:23:14,803
冒著飛行員陣亡和任務失敗的風險
Risk the lives of my pilots
and perhaps the success of this mission

1144
01:23:16,305 --> 01:23:17,306
或是
or…

1145
01:23:18,849 --> 01:23:20,309
拿我的軍旅生涯賭一把
risk my career

1146
01:23:21,393 --> 01:23:23,145
任命你為任務隊長？
by appointing you team leader?

1147
01:23:26,481 --> 01:23:27,482
長官…
Sir--

1148
01:23:27,566 --> 01:23:31,194
中將只是問問而已，上校
I think the admiral's asking a rhetorical question, Captain.

1149
01:25:12,045 --> 01:25:13,630
該怎麼辦? 呆頭鵝
Talk to me, Goose.

1150
01:25:16,967 --> 01:25:18,468
米契爾上校
Captain Mitchell!

1151
01:25:25,434 --> 01:25:27,102
你屬於這裡
You're where you belong.

1152
01:25:32,024 --> 01:25:33,525
讓我們以你為榮
Make us proud.

1153
01:25:59,635 --> 01:26:01,762
很榮幸能與你們飛行
It has been an honor flying with you.

1154
01:26:02,846 --> 01:26:06,308
每一位都是菁英中的菁英
Each one of you represents the best of the best.

1155
01:26:07,100 --> 01:26:09,811
這項任務非常艱鉅
This is a very specific mission.

1156
01:26:10,646 --> 01:26:13,941
我的選擇完全是針對任務
My choice is a reflection of that and nothing more.

1157
01:26:14,024 --> 01:26:15,859
挑選兩組F小隊隊員
Choose your two Foxtrot teams.

1158
01:26:17,444 --> 01:26:19,071
復仇者和粉弟
Payback and Fanboy.

1159
01:26:20,155 --> 01:26:21,490
鳳凰和巴布
Phoenix and Bob.

1160
01:26:25,786 --> 01:26:27,079
你的僚機駕駛員
And your wingman.

1161
01:26:31,875 --> 01:26:32,876
公雞
Rooster.

1162
01:26:37,422 --> 01:26:39,716
其他人在航母待命
The rest of you will stand by on the carrier

1163
01:26:39,800 --> 01:26:42,678
隨時準備支援
for any reserve role that's required.

1164
01:26:43,553 --> 01:26:44,721
解散
Dismissed.

1165
01:26:52,521 --> 01:26:55,357
你們的目標是迫切的威脅
Your target is a clear and present threat.

1166
01:26:56,858 --> 01:27:00,696
受到敵國掌控的秘密鈾濃縮工廠
A secret uranium enrichment site under rogue state control.

1167
01:27:01,321 --> 01:27:02,698
位於地下碉堡
It's an underground bunker,

1168
01:27:02,781 --> 01:27:04,574
坐落在這兩座山脈之間
tucked between these two mountains.

1169
01:27:06,034 --> 01:27:09,830
進攻航道受到多個防空砲台防衛
Your route of ingress is heavily defended
by surface-to-air missiles

1170
01:27:09,913 --> 01:27:12,416
另有第五代戰機支援
backed up by fifth-generation fighters.

1171
01:27:12,499 --> 01:27:15,252
F-18攻擊小隊一旦跨越邊界
Once your F-18 strike team crosses the border,

1172
01:27:15,335 --> 01:27:17,337
雷伊泰號航空母艦
Tomahawk missiles from the USS Leyte Gulf

1173
01:27:17,421 --> 01:27:21,049
就會同步發射戰斧飛彈攻擊這座機場
will launch a synchronized strike on the enemy's airfield here.

1174
01:27:22,342 --> 01:27:24,553
炸毀那裡的跑道
This will knock out their runway.

1175
01:27:26,346 --> 01:27:29,725
但你們還得對付已經升空的戰機
But you'll have to contend with any planes already in the air.

1176
01:27:29,808 --> 01:27:32,644
戰斧飛彈擊中後，敵方就知道你們來了
The moment those Tomahawks hit,
the enemy will know you're coming.

1177
01:27:33,854 --> 01:27:37,899
抵達目標時間是2分30秒
Your time to target will be two minutes and 30 seconds.

1178
01:27:39,568 --> 01:27:41,570
超過時間就會遭到
Any longer than that, and you will be exposed

1179
01:27:41,653 --> 01:27:44,281
沒被擊中的戰機攻擊
to any aircraft the Tomahawks may have missed.

1180
01:27:47,659 --> 01:27:50,078
這是你們受訓的目的
This is what you've all been training for.

1181
01:27:52,039 --> 01:27:53,540
安全回來
Come home safely.

1182
01:28:08,221 --> 01:28:09,973
讓他們好看
You give 'em hell!

1183
01:28:22,611 --> 01:28:23,612
長官
Sir.

1184
01:28:24,112 --> 01:28:25,113
長官？
Sir?

1185
01:28:27,366 --> 01:28:28,367
我…
I…

1186
01:28:31,286 --> 01:28:32,913
我只想說…
I just want to say--

1187
01:28:42,005 --> 01:28:43,340
等安全回來…
We'll talk

1188
01:28:44,841 --> 01:28:46,218
我們再聊
when we get back.

1189
01:28:52,307 --> 01:28:54,101
嘿，布雷德利！布雷德利
Hey, Bradley! Bradley!

1190
01:28:55,227 --> 01:28:56,228
嘿
Hey.

1191
01:28:59,731 --> 01:29:01,149
你行的
You got this.

1192
01:29:09,574 --> 01:29:10,575
獨行俠
Maverick.

1193
01:29:12,828 --> 01:29:13,662
獨行俠？
Maverick?

1194
01:29:15,622 --> 01:29:17,541
你在吧？
Hey, you with me?

1195
01:29:19,126 --> 01:29:20,961
我不喜歡那副表情
I don't like that look, Mav.

1196
01:29:23,797 --> 01:29:25,299
我只有這一號表情
It's the only one I got.

1197
01:29:29,928 --> 01:29:31,263
謝謝你
Thank you.

1198
01:29:32,764 --> 01:29:34,850
要是我不能再見到你，宏多…
If I don't see you again, Hondo,

1199
01:29:34,933 --> 01:29:36,268
謝謝你
thank you.

1200
01:29:44,026 --> 01:29:45,861
這是我的榮幸，上校
It's been an honor, Captain.

1201
01:30:19,019 --> 01:30:22,064
匕首一號，準備彈射
Dagger One, up and ready on Catapult One.

1202
01:30:22,147 --> 01:30:24,274
匕首候補，待命中
Dagger Spare standing by.

1203
01:30:24,358 --> 01:30:26,151
匕首四號，準備好了
Dagger Four, up and ready.

1204
01:30:26,234 --> 01:30:27,736
匕首三號，準備好了
Dagger Three, up and ready.

1205
01:30:27,819 --> 01:30:29,947
匕首二號，準備好了
Dagger Two, up and ready.

1206
01:30:31,114 --> 01:30:33,784
支援軍機起飛，攻擊小隊準備好了
Support assets airborne. Strike package ready.

1207
01:30:33,867 --> 01:30:35,744
等待起飛指令
Standing by for launch decision.

1208
01:30:36,370 --> 01:30:37,371
出發
Send them.

1209
01:30:58,016 --> 01:30:59,309
匕首二號，起飛
Dagger Two away.

1210
01:31:00,310 --> 01:31:02,271
匕首三號，起飛
Dagger Three away.

1211
01:31:02,854 --> 01:31:04,273
匕首四號，起飛
Dagger Four away.

1212
01:31:15,284 --> 01:31:17,703
偵察機，匕首一號報到
Comanche, Dagger One. Standby check in.

1213
01:31:19,079 --> 01:31:20,539
偵察機就定位
Comanche 11, set.

1214
01:31:20,622 --> 01:31:22,874
空域安全，建議匕首小隊繼續任務
Picture clean. Recommend Dagger continue.

1215
01:31:22,958 --> 01:31:24,918
收到，匕首小隊低空飛行
Copy. Daggers descending below radar.

1216
01:31:44,813 --> 01:31:47,482
匕首小隊低於雷達，切換至鷹眼影像
Daggers now below radar. Switching to E-2 picture.

1217
01:31:55,991 --> 01:31:58,577
前方是敵方領地
Here we go. Enemy territory up ahead.

1218
01:31:58,660 --> 01:32:01,622
60秒後登陸，控制中心，回報狀況
Feet dry in 60 seconds. Comanche, Dagger One. Picture.

1219
01:32:01,705 --> 01:32:04,499
前方安全，你的決定
Comanche. Picture clean. Decision is yours.

1220
01:32:04,583 --> 01:32:05,876
收到
Copy.

1221
01:32:14,176 --> 01:32:15,302
展開攻擊
Dagger attack.

1222
01:32:20,599 --> 01:32:21,892
戰斧飛彈已經發射
Tomahawks airborne.

1223
01:32:21,975 --> 01:32:24,061
沒有回頭路了
No turning back now.

1224
01:32:29,816 --> 01:32:31,860
匕首小隊，組成進攻隊形
Daggers, assume attack formation.

1225
01:32:40,953 --> 01:32:42,913
組隊飛向目標
Daggers set. Proceeding to target.

1226
01:32:42,996 --> 01:32:47,542
2分30秒，三、二、一…計時開始
Two minutes and 30 seconds in three, two, one, mark.

1227
01:32:47,626 --> 01:32:48,961
-二號計時開始
-三號計時開始
-Two mark.
-Three mark.

1228
01:32:49,044 --> 01:32:49,920
四號計時開始
Four mark.

1229
01:32:54,883 --> 01:32:55,801
進入峽谷
Going in.

1230
01:33:11,441 --> 01:33:13,652
飛過第一個砲台
First SAM site overhead.

1231
01:33:18,031 --> 01:33:19,533
我們沒被雷達偵測到
Looks like we're clear on radar, Mav.

1232
01:33:19,616 --> 01:33:21,368
別掉以輕心
Let's not take it for granted.

1233
01:33:24,871 --> 01:33:27,082
更多砲台，三點鐘方向
More SAMs! Three o'clock high!

1234
01:33:29,418 --> 01:33:31,795
-兩分鐘後抵達目標
-收到
-We got two minutes to target.
-Copy.

1235
01:33:31,878 --> 01:33:34,214
我們落後幾秒，公雞，得快點
We're a few seconds behind, Rooster. We got to move.

1236
01:33:35,757 --> 01:33:38,635
戰斧飛彈30秒後擊中跑道
Thirty seconds to Tomahawk impact on enemy airstrip.

1237
01:33:47,019 --> 01:33:48,020
匕首小隊
Dagger, Comanche.

1238
01:33:48,103 --> 01:33:50,272
我們偵測到兩架敵機
We're picking up two bandits. Single group, two contacts.

1239
01:33:50,355 --> 01:33:53,108
-它們從哪來的？
-長程巡邏？
-Where the hell'd they come from?
-Long-range patrol?

1240
01:33:58,113 --> 01:33:59,573
它們的航向是什麼？
Comanche, what's their heading?

1241
01:33:59,656 --> 01:34:02,159
航向090，目標西南50哩
Bull's-eye 090, 50, tacked southwest.

1242
01:34:02,242 --> 01:34:04,328
它們沒看到我們，飛走了
They're headed away from us. They don't know we're here.

1243
01:34:04,411 --> 01:34:06,371
戰斧飛彈一擊中空軍基地
The second those Tomahawks hit the air base,

1244
01:34:06,455 --> 01:34:08,624
敵機就會折返防衛目標
those bandits are gonna move to defend the target.

1245
01:34:08,707 --> 01:34:11,293
我們得搶先一步，加速
We have to get there before they do. Increase speed.

1246
01:34:12,669 --> 01:34:14,963
我們會跟上，別等我
We got you, Mav. Don't wait for me.

1247
01:34:20,927 --> 01:34:23,930
匕首二號和四號進度落後
Sir, Daggers Two and Four are behind schedule.

1248
01:34:24,014 --> 01:34:26,016
抵達目標時間，1分20秒
Time to target, one minute 20.

1249
01:34:27,225 --> 01:34:29,394
戰斧飛彈將於三、二…
Tomahawk impact in three, two…

1250
01:34:33,774 --> 01:34:36,234
擊中目標，機場跑道全毀
Impact. Enemy runway is destroyed.

1251
01:34:37,027 --> 01:34:38,695
他們知道我們來了
They know we're coming now.

1252
01:34:42,074 --> 01:34:44,409
敵機轉向前去保護目標
Bandits are switching course to defend the target.

1253
01:34:44,493 --> 01:34:45,619
公雞，你在哪裡？
Rooster, where are you?

1254
01:34:47,329 --> 01:34:49,081
快點，敵機來襲
Come on, Rooster. Bandits inbound.

1255
01:34:49,164 --> 01:34:51,333
我們得趕上，快加速
We got to make up time now. Let's turn and burn.

1256
01:34:59,299 --> 01:35:00,342
小心，鳳凰
Heads up, Phoenix.

1257
01:35:10,143 --> 01:35:14,523
敵機距離目標兩分鐘，匕首小隊一分鐘
Sir, bandits are two minutes from target.
Daggers are one minute from target.

1258
01:35:14,606 --> 01:35:16,900
快啊，公雞，不快點就會死
Come on, Rooster. Move it or lose it.

1259
01:35:19,152 --> 01:35:21,989
我們落後了，真的得加速
Guys, we're falling behind. We really got to move.

1260
01:35:22,072 --> 01:35:23,865
現在不加速
If we don't increase our speed right now,

1261
01:35:23,949 --> 01:35:26,743
敵機就會在目標那裡等著我們
those bandits are gonna be waiting for us
when we reach the target.

1262
01:35:28,537 --> 01:35:29,746
爸，該怎麼做？
Talk to me, Dad.

1263
01:35:31,081 --> 01:35:32,582
加油，你行的，別猶豫
Come on, kid, you can do it.

1264
01:35:32,666 --> 01:35:34,710
放手去做
Don't think, just do.

1265
01:35:43,218 --> 01:35:44,678
天啊，別那麼快
Jesus, Rooster, not that fast!

1266
01:35:44,761 --> 01:35:47,306
這就對了，咱們上吧
That's it, kid, that's it. All right, let's go.

1267
01:35:51,393 --> 01:35:53,145
該死，公雞，慢一點
Damn, Rooster, take it easy.

1268
01:35:53,812 --> 01:35:56,440
匕首二號趕上來了
Sir, Dagger Two is reengaging.

1269
01:35:56,523 --> 01:35:58,900
很好，擊中目標就回來
All right, now hit your target and come home.

1270
01:36:03,322 --> 01:36:06,033
30秒後抵達目標，巴布，檢查雷射
Thirty seconds to target. Bob, check your laser.

1271
01:36:06,116 --> 01:36:09,620
檢查完畢，確認雷射辨識碼1688
Air-to-ground check complete. Laser code verified, 1688.

1272
01:36:09,703 --> 01:36:10,787
雷射待命中
Laser is a go!

1273
01:36:13,123 --> 01:36:14,499
小心
Watch your heads.

1274
01:36:16,251 --> 01:36:17,711
哇靠
Holy shit!

1275
01:36:17,794 --> 01:36:19,713
-復仇者，跟上了嗎？
-在你後方
-Payback, you with me?
-Right behind you.

1276
01:36:20,797 --> 01:36:22,633
鳳凰，準備攻擊
Phoenix, stand by for pop-up strike.

1277
01:36:22,716 --> 01:36:24,051
匕首三號就位
Dagger Three in position.

1278
01:36:24,718 --> 01:36:27,387
倒數三、二、一，爬升
Popping in three, two, one.

1279
01:36:55,415 --> 01:36:57,668
-標示目標，巴布
-匕首三號
-Get me eyes on that target, Bob.
-Dagger Three.

1280
01:36:58,543 --> 01:36:59,836
待命
Stand by, Mav.

1281
01:36:59,920 --> 01:37:02,339
-快啊，巴布
-待命
-Come on, Bob, come on.
-Stand by.

1282
01:37:02,923 --> 01:37:05,676
-標示目標了
-鎖定目標，投擲炸彈
-I've got it. Captured!
-Target acquired. Bombs away.

1283
01:37:26,738 --> 01:37:30,117
擊中了，確認命中目標
We've got impact! Check, direct hit! Direct hit!

1284
01:37:30,200 --> 01:37:32,035
那是第一個奇蹟
That's miracle number one.

1285
01:37:32,703 --> 01:37:34,121
匕首二號，回報
Dagger Two, status.

1286
01:37:34,204 --> 01:37:35,706
就快到了，獨行俠，就快到了
Almost there, Mav. Almost there.

1287
01:37:38,375 --> 01:37:39,960
粉弟，雷射咧？
Fanboy, where's my laser?

1288
01:37:40,544 --> 01:37:42,671
雷射出了狀況
Rooster, there's something wrong with this laser.

1289
01:37:42,754 --> 01:37:44,381
靠，雷射失靈…
Shit! Deadeye, deadeye, deadeye!

1290
01:37:44,464 --> 01:37:46,800
快點，沒時間了，快點搞定
Come on, guys, we're running out of time. Get it online!

1291
01:37:46,883 --> 01:37:48,343
-我正在試
-快點，粉弟
-I'm trying!
-Come on, Fanboy!

1292
01:37:48,427 --> 01:37:50,095
就快好了，快好了！
Nearly there! Nearly there!

1293
01:37:58,979 --> 01:38:01,565
-快啊
-來不及了，我要隨意投擲
-Come on, Fanboy, get it online.
-There's no time. I'm dropping blind.

1294
01:38:01,648 --> 01:38:03,859
-公雞，我行的
-來不及了，快走
-Rooster, I got this!
-No time. Pull up.

1295
01:38:03,942 --> 01:38:05,319
-等等
-投擲炸彈！投擲炸彈
-Wait!
-Bombs away! Bombs away!

1296
01:38:18,874 --> 01:38:20,709
正中目標！
Bull's-eye, bull's-eye, bull's-eye!

1297
01:38:24,671 --> 01:38:25,964
第二個奇蹟
Miracle number two.

1298
01:38:26,048 --> 01:38:27,674
他們飛到棺材角
Now they're in Coffin Corner.

1299
01:38:27,758 --> 01:38:29,843
還沒脫險
We're not out of this yet.

1300
01:38:31,678 --> 01:38:33,096
大家小心
Here it comes.

1301
01:38:36,141 --> 01:38:38,310
飛彈來襲，鳳凰，向右急轉
Radar warning! Smoke in the air. Phoenix, break right.

1302
01:38:38,393 --> 01:38:40,687
匕首三號發射誘彈
Emergency jettison. Dagger Three defending.

1303
01:38:40,771 --> 01:38:42,564
又來一枚飛彈
Here comes another one!

1304
01:38:42,648 --> 01:38:44,316
匕首一號發射誘彈
Dagger One defending.

1305
01:38:50,614 --> 01:38:51,698
公雞，回報
Rooster, status.

1306
01:38:59,915 --> 01:39:00,916
天啊
Oh, my God.

1307
01:39:03,126 --> 01:39:04,544
飛彈來襲
Smoke in the air!

1308
01:39:05,921 --> 01:39:07,798
-向右急轉
-Break right, Payback!
-Breaking right.

1309
01:39:09,216 --> 01:39:11,051
天啊，又來了
Oh, my God, here they come!

1310
01:39:11,134 --> 01:39:12,511
公雞，飛彈在你正後方
SAM on your six, Rooster!

1311
01:39:13,971 --> 01:39:15,347
發射反制火焰彈
Deploying countermeasures.

1312
01:39:18,183 --> 01:39:19,685
我沒被擊中
Negative contact.

1313
01:39:21,728 --> 01:39:22,813
匕首一號進行迴避
Dagger One defending.

1314
01:39:24,231 --> 01:39:27,109
-回報狀況，巴布
-鳳凰、獨行俠，向右急轉
-Talk to me, Bob.
-Break right, Phoenix! Break right! Mav!

1315
01:39:27,192 --> 01:39:28,694
九點鐘方向！九點鐘方向
Nine o'clock! Nine o'clock!

1316
01:39:29,528 --> 01:39:31,488
公雞，兩枚在你正後方
Rooster, two more on your six.

1317
01:39:31,571 --> 01:39:33,031
匕首二號發射誘彈
Dagger Two, defending.

1318
01:39:37,619 --> 01:39:39,955
-復仇者，正前方
-發射誘彈
-Payback, SAM on your nose.
-Dagger Four defending.

1319
01:39:40,038 --> 01:39:41,623
-七點鐘方向
-回報狀況，巴布
-Rooster, tally, seven o'clock!
-Talk to me, Bob!

1320
01:39:41,707 --> 01:39:43,041
-正後方
-匕首二號發射誘彈
-On our six!
-Dagger Two defending.

1321
01:39:43,125 --> 01:39:44,793
-向右急轉
-我看到了
-Phoenix, break right!
-I see it!

1322
01:39:52,175 --> 01:39:53,552
匕首二號發射誘彈
Dagger Two defending.

1323
01:39:54,928 --> 01:39:56,096
靠，我沒誘彈了
Shit, I'm out of flares!

1324
01:39:56,179 --> 01:39:58,515
公雞，迴避
Rooster, evade, evade!

1325
01:39:58,598 --> 01:40:00,851
甩不掉它們！它們鎖定我了
它們鎖定我了
I can't shake 'em! They're on me! They're on me!

1326
01:40:10,986 --> 01:40:12,613
獨行俠，不！
Mav! No!

1327
01:40:14,615 --> 01:40:18,118
匕首一號中彈，重複，匕首一號中彈
Dagger One is hit! I repeat, Dagger One is hit!

1328
01:40:18,201 --> 01:40:19,703
獨行俠被擊落
Maverick is down.

1329
01:40:19,786 --> 01:40:20,954
匕首一號，回報
Dagger One, status.

1330
01:40:21,038 --> 01:40:22,664
回報！
Status!

1331
01:40:22,748 --> 01:40:24,875
有誰看到他？
Anyone see him? Does anyone see him?

1332
01:40:24,958 --> 01:40:27,169
-匕首一號，回報
-沒看到降落傘
-Dagger One, come in!
-I didn't see a parachute.

1333
01:40:27,294 --> 01:40:28,920
我們得繞回去
We have to circle back.

1334
01:40:29,004 --> 01:40:31,506
敵機來襲，準備攻擊
Comanche. Bandits inbound. Single group, hot.

1335
01:40:31,590 --> 01:40:33,091
建議匕首小隊往南飛
Recommend Dagger flow south.

1336
01:40:33,925 --> 01:40:35,927
一分鐘後攔截
One minute to intercept.

1337
01:40:39,181 --> 01:40:40,766
快叫他們飛返航母
Get 'em back to the carrier now.

1338
01:40:40,849 --> 01:40:43,352
敵機來襲，匕首小隊飛返基地
All Daggers flow to ECP. You have bandits headed for you.

1339
01:40:43,435 --> 01:40:44,478
獨行俠呢？
What about Maverick?

1340
01:40:44,561 --> 01:40:47,564
跟他說他也無能為力，F-18打不過敵機
Tell him there's nothing he can do
for Maverick, not in a goddamn F-18.

1341
01:40:47,648 --> 01:40:50,484
匕首後備要求進行空中支援
Dagger Spare request permission to launch and fly air cover.

1342
01:40:52,778 --> 01:40:53,779
不准
Negative, Spare.

1343
01:40:54,947 --> 01:40:57,491
-展開搜救行動
-不行，空中有敵機
-Launch search and rescue.
-Negative. Not with bandits in the air.

1344
01:40:57,574 --> 01:41:01,119
-獨行俠還活著
-今天不能再損失任何人
-But, sir, Maverick is still out there.
-We are not losing anyone else today.

1345
01:41:03,080 --> 01:41:04,581
命令他們回來
Get 'em home now.

1346
01:41:04,665 --> 01:41:07,209
匕首小隊，不准救援
Dagger, you are not to engage.

1347
01:41:07,292 --> 01:41:09,378
重複，不准救援
Repeat, do not engage.

1348
01:41:09,461 --> 01:41:12,547
匕首二號飛返航母，確認
Dagger Two, return to carrier. Acknowledge.

1349
01:41:12,631 --> 01:41:13,632
確認
Acknowledge.

1350
01:41:13,715 --> 01:41:17,177
公雞，敵機逼近，不能回去
Rooster, those bandits are closing. We can't go back.

1351
01:41:17,260 --> 01:41:20,138
公雞，他死了
Rooster, he's gone.

1352
01:41:21,807 --> 01:41:23,308
獨行俠死了
Maverick's gone.

1353
01:42:53,774 --> 01:42:54,775
噢，不…
Oh, no, no.

1354
01:43:01,531 --> 01:43:02,991
匕首二號被擊中
Dagger Two is hit.

1355
01:43:04,159 --> 01:43:05,243
匕首二號被擊中
Dagger Two is hit.

1356
01:43:06,828 --> 01:43:08,205
匕首二號，回報
Dagger Two, come in.

1357
01:43:09,915 --> 01:43:11,750
匕首二號，收到嗎？
Dagger Two, do you copy?

1358
01:43:12,417 --> 01:43:14,711
匕首二號，回報
Dagger Two, come in.

1359
01:43:39,987 --> 01:43:41,196
你沒事吧？
You all right?

1360
01:43:41,280 --> 01:43:42,864
我沒事，你呢？
Yeah, I'm good. You all right?

1361
01:43:45,450 --> 01:43:46,535
搞什麼鬼？
What the hell?

1362
01:43:46,618 --> 01:43:48,996
-你來幹嘛？
-我來幹嘛？
-What are you doing here?
-What am I doing here?

1363
01:43:49,079 --> 01:43:51,456
我替你擋飛彈不是讓你也落難
You think I took that missile
so you could be down here with me?

1364
01:43:51,540 --> 01:43:53,375
你早就該飛返航母了
You should be back on the carrier by now!

1365
01:43:53,458 --> 01:43:55,168
我救了你一命
I saved your life!

1366
01:43:55,294 --> 01:43:58,380
我救了你，那才是重點
I saved your life. That's the whole point.

1367
01:43:58,463 --> 01:44:00,257
你到底在想什麼？
What the hell were you even thinking?

1368
01:44:00,340 --> 01:44:02,384
你叫我不要想
You told me not to think!

1369
01:44:19,109 --> 01:44:20,193
這樣嘛…
Well,

1370
01:44:21,528 --> 01:44:22,904
見到你真好
it's good to see you.

1371
01:44:25,324 --> 01:44:26,950
我也是
It's good to see you too.

1372
01:44:30,996 --> 01:44:32,456
有什麼計畫？
So what's the plan?

1373
01:44:43,425 --> 01:44:44,801
不是吧
You're not serious.

1374
01:45:00,317 --> 01:45:01,944
你在開玩笑吧
You've got to be shitting me.

1375
01:45:03,946 --> 01:45:04,988
F-14戰機？
An F-14?

1376
01:45:05,697 --> 01:45:07,491
我開那玩意擊落三架米格機
I shot down three MiGs in one of those.

1377
01:45:07,574 --> 01:45:09,993
那古董能不能飛都不知道
We don't even know if that bag of ass can fly.

1378
01:45:12,704 --> 01:45:14,665
-試試就知道
-獨行俠
-Let's find out.
-Mav!

1379
01:45:16,541 --> 01:45:17,542
好吧
Okay.

1380
01:45:27,094 --> 01:45:29,096
-前面有人
-是啊
-There's guys up there, Mav.
-Yeah.

1381
01:45:30,347 --> 01:45:32,265
-那裡有更多人
-好吧
-There's more over there.
-Okay.

1382
01:45:33,558 --> 01:45:35,727
-開始跑吧
-好啊，跑，跑啊
-Let's start running.
-Yeah, run. Run.

1383
01:45:45,195 --> 01:45:47,572
我會打信號要你充氣
Once I give you the signal for air,

1384
01:45:48,282 --> 01:45:50,993
打開這開關直到針頭指到120
you're gonna flip this switch until the needle gets to 120.

1385
01:45:51,076 --> 01:45:52,244
引擎啟動後
When the engine starts,

1386
01:45:52,327 --> 01:45:54,830
馬上拔除一切
you got to pull out the pins and disconnect everything.

1387
01:45:54,913 --> 01:45:56,581
-你瞭嗎？
-我瞭
-You understand?
-Yeah.

1388
01:45:58,750 --> 01:45:59,751
好耶！
Yes!

1389
01:46:01,628 --> 01:46:03,797
我一上去就收起梯子
Once I'm up, stow the ladder.

1390
01:46:11,722 --> 01:46:13,765
好吧，哇塞
Okay. Wow.

1391
01:46:14,933 --> 01:46:16,768
很久沒開了
It's been a minute, huh, Mav?

1392
01:46:45,631 --> 01:46:48,592
天啊，這玩意超老舊的
Oh, my God. This thing is so old.

1393
01:46:49,593 --> 01:46:50,594
好吧
All right.

1394
01:46:55,682 --> 01:46:57,225
-關閉座艙罩
-好
-Canopy?
-Clear.

1395
01:47:15,452 --> 01:47:17,329
兩條跑道都被炸毀
Both runways are cratered.

1396
01:47:18,038 --> 01:47:20,123
該怎麼讓這老古董起飛？
How we gonna get this museum piece in the air?

1397
01:47:30,509 --> 01:47:31,927
你為什麼延展機翼？
Why are the wings coming out, Mav?

1398
01:47:38,600 --> 01:47:41,311
這是滑行道，不是跑道
Mav, this is a taxiway, not a runway.

1399
01:47:41,895 --> 01:47:44,815
而且是很短的滑行道
This is a very short taxiway, Mav.

1400
01:47:44,898 --> 01:47:46,108
坐好了
Just hang on.

1401
01:47:47,442 --> 01:47:48,819
哇咧！
Holy shit!

1402
01:47:54,866 --> 01:47:56,159
快點，快點
Come on, come on, come on.

1403
01:47:56,243 --> 01:47:57,286
指針能運作
Needle's alive.

1404
01:48:00,706 --> 01:48:02,958
-獨行俠？
-很好，快點…
-Mav?
-That's it. Come on, come on!

1405
01:48:03,041 --> 01:48:04,084
好吧
All right.

1406
01:48:05,002 --> 01:48:07,004
-獨行俠
-起飛囉
-Mav!
-Here we go.

1407
01:48:08,463 --> 01:48:09,881
天啊
Holy shit.

1408
01:48:23,645 --> 01:48:26,732
長官，收到公雞的信號
Sir, we're receiving a signal from Rooster's ESAT.

1409
01:48:26,815 --> 01:48:28,734
看起來是故障
But there seems to be a malfunction.

1410
01:48:28,817 --> 01:48:30,152
-信號又消失了？
-不是
-Have you lost him?
-No, sir.

1411
01:48:31,153 --> 01:48:32,613
他進入超音速
He's supersonic.

1412
01:48:33,238 --> 01:48:34,323
他在飛行
He's airborne.

1413
01:48:35,574 --> 01:48:37,159
-用什麼飛？
-長官
-In what?
-Sir.

1414
01:48:37,868 --> 01:48:42,122
偵察機回報一架F-14戰機正在飛來
Overwatch reports an F-14 Tomcat is
airborne and on course for our position.

1415
01:48:43,040 --> 01:48:45,584
不可能，不可能
Can't be. It can't be!

1416
01:48:47,294 --> 01:48:48,295
是獨行俠
Maverick.

1417
01:48:50,547 --> 01:48:52,883
公雞，快聯絡航母
Okay, Rooster, get us in touch with the boat.

1418
01:48:52,966 --> 01:48:54,426
我正在試
I'm working on it.

1419
01:48:54,509 --> 01:48:57,929
